Ryze.start01.text: "I find the runes so they won't be found by someone else - or some thing."

Ryze.start02.text: "The things I've seen in the dark corners of Runeterra are better left unseen."

Ryze.start03.text: "Things to do today: find food, build shelter, fix the world."

Ryze.start05.text: "Can we make this quick? I have some place to be!"

Ryze.start06.text: "If I sound rude, it's because I've got a world to save."

Ryze.move01.text: "These runes are not for eyes such as yours."

Ryze.move02.text: "They know so little of the world they traverse."

Ryze.move04.text: "I work alone. Company weighs me down."

Ryze.move05.text: "What's on my back? That's not your concern."

Ryze.move07.text: "Every rune I find is another day we live."

Ryze.move09.text: "They have forgotten the fires that forged this world."

Ryze.move10.text: "You know what I could use? An ale."

Ryze.move11.text: "They want to read my scroll. It'll be the last thing they read."

Ryze.move12.text: "I could tell you what's on this scroll, but then I'd have to obliterate you."

Ryze.move14.text: "I dream in nightmares of the past."

Ryze.move15.text: "None are worthy of my task... even me."

Ryze.move16.text: "Everyone is doomed to repeat history. That's where I come in."

Ryze.move18.text: "I may fail, but I won't quit."

Ryze.move19.text: "Trust no-one, especially those who seek power."

Ryze.move20.text: "Just once I'd like a good night's sleep."

Ryze.move21.text: "Their minds couldn't handle what my eyes have seen."

Ryze.move22.text: "I care about these mortals. That's why I keep them at arm's length."

Ryze.move23.text: "In an instant, all could be gone."

Ryze.move24.text: "I long for the day when this is all over."

Ryze.move26.text: "Everyone wants to chat when you're busy saving the world."

Ryze.move28.text: "You know what I miss? Standing still."

Ryze.move29.text: "All that binds this world is will."

Ryze.move30.text: "Magic dooms us... but perhaps it can save us."

Ryze.move33.text: "One can only hold all this power for so long."

Ryze.move34.text: "If I had a rune for every mile I've run, I'd be done running."

Ryze.move35.text: "You want to help? Get out of the way."

Ryze.move36.text: "I remember when only one world weighed on my shoulders."

Ryze.move37.text: "When I've found them all, I'll fade away."

Ryze.move38.text: "If I fall, the scroll must be destroyed."

Ryze.move39.text: "I fight so they don't have to."

Ryze.move43.text: "My story? That would take ages to tell."

Ryze.move44.text: "Consider yourself lucky for the days you have."

Ryze.move46.text: "Fast and lean, that's how I travel."

Ryze.move47.text: "Ah, civilization. I remember when I was a part of it."

Ryze.move50.text: "All this would be so much easier if I didn't give a damn."

Ryze.taunt01.text: "Hm. I'm hunted by things far worse than you."

Ryze.taunt02.text: "I'm no doctor, but I think there's a spell for what you have."

Ryze.taunt03.text: "To be ignorant is to be free. You must be very free."

Ryze.taunt04.text: "If I had a tattoo that looked like you, I'd get it removed."

Ryze.taunt05.text: "There's gonna be two sounds - me hitting you, and you disintegrating."

Ryze.tauntNoxian01.text: "You wage your petty war, Noxian, but the real war is yet to come."

Ryze.tauntYordle01.text: "Even your kind will know death in the cataclysm."

Ryze.tauntAhri01.text: "Your charms are impressive, but I'm not into forest creatures."

Ryze.tauntAnnie01.text: "Run along, child, this tome is not a bedtime story."

Ryze.tauntAurelionSol01.text: "Space called, it wants its arrogant jerk back."

Ryze.tauntBard01.text: "I don't suppose you'd want to get off your magical rear and help me save this world."

Ryze.tauntDrMundo01.text: "I have a hard time believing you went to medical school."

Ryze.tauntGraves01.text: "I would chide you for your idiocy, but you seem pretty proud of it."

Ryze.tauntIllaoi01.text: "Nice tattoos, do they conduct runic energy? No? Oh, that's too bad."

Ryze.tauntLux01.text: "Magic is more than sunshine and rainbows, girl."

Ryze.tauntMalzahar01.text: "Hey, you're the one who summons bloodthirsty Void creatures, right? Yeah, brilliant work, good thinking."

Ryze.tauntTwistedFate01.text: "Nice card trick, do you do birthday parties?"

Ryze.tauntXerath01.text: "That remarkable arcane energy doesn't run through your entire body, does it?"

Ryze.interactionTauntEnemy01.text: "We'll see how smart your mouth is when the world collapses."

Ryze.interactionTauntEnemy02.text: "I'm surprised you can string enough words together for that one. You need a break?"

Ryze.interactionTauntEnemy03.text: "So that's what you people do with your spare time."

Ryze.interactionTauntEnemy04.text: "Not going to dignify that with a response."

Ryze.interactionTauntEnemy05.text: "You should read more, expand your vocabulary."

Ryze.joke01.text: "What? You want to see a magic trick? Fine... tada."

Ryze.joke02.text: "Okay, fine, here's a magic trick. Tada."

Ryze.spreeKillingSpree02.text: "Better a few perish than the entire world."

Ryze.spreeKillingSpree03.text: "I tried to warn them, I really did."
Ryze.spreeKillingSpree03.trigger: Upon Going on a Killing Spree

Ryze.recall01.text: "A pause in the chaos. Let's make it count."

Evelynn.attack02.text: ​"Ooh, you're so hot when you're hurt."

Evelynn.attack08.text: "Like what you see? I'll rip off your eyelids!"

Evelynn.attack11.text: "I can't wait to see your pain face."

Evelynn.attack16.text: "I know you're hurting, but I can't feel without this."

Evelynn.attack17.text: "Everyone's pain tastes different. What flavor is yours?"

Evelynn.attack18.text: "Awww, you thought you were getting lucky!"

Evelynn.attack38.text: "Nothing personal, I just need you to suffer horribly."

Evelynn.attack39.text: "The more I cut away, the closer we'll get."

Evelynn.attackDragon1.text: "Not the first time I've had dragon."

Evelynn.attackDragon2.text: "What a magnificent creature... Let's kill it slowly!"

Evelynn.attackDragon3.text: "Don't worry honey, I'm open to all types."

Evelynn.attackBaron3.text: "The bigger they are, the more places you can hurt them."

Evelynn.attackBaron4.text: "Finally! A man who can satisfy me."

Evelynn.move01.text: ​"Hate? No! I hurt them out of love."

Evelynn.move02.text: "I feel their looks like hot breath. They feel my claws like hot knives."

Evelynn.move05.text: ​"Just looking for that special someone to torment."

Evelynn.move06.text: ​"I can't feel anything... until they do."

Evelynn.move07.text: ​"Every smile is just a frown waiting to be turned upside down."

Evelynn.move08.text: ​"The height of their happiness is the depth of their pain."

Evelynn.move10.text: ​"Hate and love are just two words for passion."

Evelynn.move11.text: "I was born of a thousand screams. What's one more?"

Evelynn.move12.text: ​"Their mouths say no, but their bodies say "flay me alive.""

Evelynn.move13.text: "Drink the pain, toss away the rest."

Evelynn.move14.text: ​"Once I was overwhelmed by the agony. Now I can't get enough."

Evelynn.move15.text: ​"You really don't know someone 'til you've seen them beg for mercy."

Evelynn.move16.text: ​"I like the happy ones. They have so much farther to fall."

Evelynn.move17.text: ​"Without pain, how would they know pleasure?"

Evelynn.move18.text: ​"I hurt them 'til they hurt no more."

Evelynn.move19.text: ​"Misery loves whatever I tell it to."

Evelynn.move20.text: "One touch, with desire... that's all I need."

Evelynn.move21.text: ​"Someday they'll love me for who I really am."

Evelynn.move23.text: ​"Suffering is the meaning of life. Well... their lives."

Evelynn.move24.text: ​"Let's see... something to fill the emptiness..."

Evelynn.move25.text: ​"I remember when just a little pain did the trick."

Evelynn.move26.text: "Rend their flesh, flay them head to toe."

Evelynn.move27.text: ​"Girls just wanna tear your throat out with their teeth."

Evelynn.move29.text: "Need to find me? Just follow the trail of widows."

Evelynn.move30.text: ​"I use every part of their torment. Nothing is wasted."

Evelynn.move31.text: "I don't break hearts. I just tear them from rib cages."

Evelynn.move32.text: ​"They're all my favorites... until they break."

Evelynn.move33.text: ​"Through suffering they come to love me. Every. Single. One."

Evelynn.move36.text: ​"A man once told me to put on some clothes. So I wore his skin."

Evelynn.move37.text: "Who does a girl have to kill to start another Rune War?"

Evelynn.move39.text: "Always dress like you're seducing your next victim."

Evelynn.move40.text: "Ah, how their screams make me tingle."

Evelynn.move41.text: "Don't try to tell me I'm not gorgeous."

Evelynn.move42.text: "Every kill is just a lover who didn't work out."

Evelynn.move43.text: "People have too many emotions. What am I supposed to do with "empathy?""

Evelynn.move44.text: "I tasted peace once. Didn't do it for me."

Evelynn.firstMove1.text: ​"Let's see... whose life shall I ruin today?"
Evelynn.firstMove1.trigger: Upon Moving for the First Time

Evelynn.firstMove2.text: "The moment they think they have me..." Evelynn laughs. "Yeah, that's what I live for."
Evelynn.firstMove2.trigger: Upon Moving for the First Time

Evelynn.firstMove3.text: ​"This place is so bland. It needs a splash of red."
Evelynn.firstMove3.trigger: Upon Moving for the First Time

Evelynn.firstMove4.text: "Show me the man who has everything, and I'll show you my next victim."
Evelynn.firstMove4.trigger: Upon Moving for the First Time

Evelynn.firstMove5.text: ​"Oooh, so many joyful people to hurt."
Evelynn.firstMove5.trigger: Upon Moving for the First Time

Evelynn.joke1.text: ​"I love it when they talk dirty. "No! Please! Stop torturing me!"" Evelynn laughs.

Evelynn.jokeResponse1.text: ​"Know what else is funny? Pulling your tongue out through your neck."

Evelynn.taunt1.text: ​"I've had my eye on you. Now I'm gonna rip yours out."

Evelynn.taunt2.text: "First time being tortured? Don't worry, I'll do everything."

Evelynn.taunt3.text: ​"I'll suck every last drop of joy from your heart."

Evelynn.taunt4.text: ​"That skin looks good on you, but it would look better on my bedroom floor."

Evelynn.tauntResponse1.text: "Naughty, naughty. That gets you a lashing."

Evelynn.allyTauntResponse1.text: ​"I don't really have friends. Just people I haven't eviscerated yet."

Evelynn.tauntAmumu2.text: ​"Ugh. I wouldn't torture you if you were the last person on earth."

Evelynn.tauntAurelionSol1.text: "With infinite power comes an infinite capacity for pain."

Evelynn.tauntBard1.text: "I can make you do a lot more than jingle, space man."

Evelynn.tauntDrMundo1.text: ​"So, you're a masochist? Whatcha doing later?"

Evelynn.tauntLeeSin1.text: ​"Blindfolds, huh? Whatever does it for ya."

Evelynn.tauntLowerLifeForm1.text: ​"Can your kind even feel? I don't want to waste my time."
Evelynn.tauntLowerLifeForm1.trigger: Upon Taunting Lower Life Forms ( Orianna, Gnar, Kog'Maw, Rek'Sai, Twitch, etc.)

Evelynn.tauntLucian1.text: ​"I've seen your wife. You can do better."

Evelynn.tauntMuscularChamp1.text: ​"Just the way I like 'em. Big and stupid."
Evelynn.tauntMuscularChamp1.trigger: Upon Taunting Muscular Champs ( Braum, Darius, Illaoi, etc.)

Evelynn.tauntNocturne1.text: ​"Why don't we leave the lights on for this?"

Evelynn.tauntTahmKench1.text: ​"So how are you, River King? I see you haven't missed a meal."

Evelynn.tauntTahmKench2.text: ​"I like your style, Kench, but stay out of my territory."

Evelynn.tauntTank1.text: ​"You look like someone I could hurt for days."
Evelynn.tauntTank1.trigger: Upon Taunting Tanks ( Alistar, Blitzcrank, Jarvan IV, Nautilus, Sejuani, etc.)

Evelynn.tauntThresh2.text: ​"How do you kill them so slowly? You have to teach me."

Evelynn.tauntVayne1.text: ​"Have I told you how your parents cried with their final breaths?"

Evelynn.tauntVayne2.text: ​"Don't worry, love. You'll join them soon."

Evelynn.enterDemonShade03.text: "Mind if I slip into something a little more... painful?"

Evelynn.enterDemonShade07.text: "The things we whisper in the dark."

Evelynn.enterDemonShade10.text: "They can touch, but they can't look."

Evelynn.enterDemonShade11.text: "They all look the same in the dark."

Evelynn.enterDemonShade12.text: "What they don't know won't hurt them... yet."

Evelynn.castAllure01.text: "The things I'm going to do to you."

Evelynn.castAllure02.text: "That's it, love. Let your guard down."

Evelynn.castAllure05.text: "Ooh, are you lonely? I can help."

Evelynn.castAllure06.text: "A little bit of heaven before the hell."

Evelynn.kill02.text: ​Evelynn makes a noise of disappointment. "I hate it when they don't last."

Evelynn.kill04.text: ​"Look at me! I need to watch you go."

Evelynn.kill06.text: "Ugh... I think we should break up."

Evelynn.kill07.text: ​"Oh well... Time to find a new toy."

Evelynn.kill12.text: "Was it as good for you as it was for me? No? Too bad!"

Evelynn.kill14.text: "We need to talk. I want to kill other people."

Evelynn.buyClothArmor2.text: "It's a sin to cover something so perfect."

Evelynn.buyClothArmor3.text: "Why not give them something to take off?"

Evelynn.buyRabadonsDeathcap1.text: "Hello, hat. Ready to feast on the pain of others?"

Evelynn.buyRabadonsDeathcap2.text: "This land will become a sea of torment."

Evelynn.buyLichBane2.text: "The pain of a lich is eternal."

Evelynn.buyVoidStaff1.text: "Imagine what we can do with this."

Evelynn.buyVoidStaff3.text: "Think of all the places this can go."

Evelynn.buyLiandrysTorment1.text: "Aahh, still wet with the tears of Liandry herself."

Evelynn.buyLiandrysTorment2.text: "I do like your style Liandry, whoever you were."

Evelynn.buyLiandrysTorment3.text: "Now they will all know true pain."

Evelynn.recall01.text: ​"A girl's gotta know when to disappear."

Evelynn.recall02.text: ​"Be right back. Gotta put my face on."

Taric.start01.text: "There's nowhere left to go but up."

Taric.start02.text: "I have risen beyond the call of banners and kings."

Taric.start03.text: "There is great power in the stars. Great danger as well."

Taric.start04.text: "The most precious jewel is the one we hold in our heart."

Taric.start05.text: "The climb may be long, but the view is worth it."

Taric.attack05.text: "Beauty can stir one's heart... or stop it."

Taric.attack14.text: "I climbed Mount Targon. You did not."

Taric.attack16.text: "I find all life beautiful... except yours."

Taric.attack17.text: "This world's fragile beauty must be preserved."

Taric.attack18.text: "The stars keep the darkness at bay."

Taric.attackBaron01.text: "You seem to have too many heads. Let's see if I can help you with that."

Taric.attackBaron02.text: "I know I'm supposed to cherish all life, but come on."

Taric.attackBaron03.text: "The taint of the Void is upon you."

Taric.attackDragon01.text: "Nothing personal, but you've got to go."

Taric.move01.text: "I may be merciful, but Targon isn't."

Taric.move04.text: "The stars were the question. I was the answer."

Taric.move05.text: "The mountain's mysteries are known to me."

Taric.move06.text: "Why is it always the ugly ones?"

Taric.move07.text: "Easy on the eyes? Don't I know it."

Taric.move09.text: "I am no longer the man I once was."

Taric.move10.text: "We're all headed toward the same inevitable end. No need to rush."

Taric.move11.text: "Demacia was my home, but the stars are my destination."

Taric.move12.text: "I have seen the light too clearly to ever fear the darkness."

Taric.move13.text: "The mountain reveals the harshest truths in our souls."

Taric.move14.text: "Human life is fleeting, a mountain's life less so, but stars... stars are eternal."

Taric.move16.text: "My heart is filled with starlight. I give it freely to all."

Taric.move18.text: "Truth is worth fighting for, but beauty is worth dying for."

Taric.move19.text: "True gems sparkle even in the absence of light."

Taric.move20.text: "Elegance never helped win a fight, but it never hurt."

Taric.move22.text: "To truly see the stars, I climbed."

Taric.move23.text: "We see beauty in the stars, and they see beauty in us."

Taric.move24.text: "Just as the mountain is eternal, so is hope."

Taric.move26.text: "The mountain's question is unique for each of us."

Taric.taunt01.text: "I answered for my crimes. Now it's your turn."

Taric.taunt03.text: "I bested the mountain. Now it's your turn."

Taric.tauntAshe01.text: "That bow is of the stars, as is its mistress."

Taric.tauntDiana01.text: "Own your destiny, or it will own you."

Taric.tauntDiana02.text: "Who could have guessed the Aspect of the Moon would be so beautiful?"

Taric.tauntGaren01.text: "I will never turn my back on Demacia."

Taric.tauntGaren02.text: "Good to see you again, old friend."

Taric.tauntVoidborn01.text: "I will purge the Void from this world."

Taric.tauntVelKoz01.text: "They say beauty is in the eye of the beholder."

Taric.tauntVelKoz02.text: "I will enjoy sending you back to the Void. In pieces."

Taric.tauntJhin01.text: "The heavens see all you have done."

Taric.tauntLeona01.text: "The sun is but a traveller through the kingdom of the stars."

Taric.tauntTahmKench01.text: "You are weighed down by your petty hungers."

Taric.tauntTaric01.text: "I like the cut of your gem."

Taric.joke01.text: "I've been to the top of the mountain... and the bottom of the gutter. There's much to learn from both."

Taric.joke02.text: "Beauty can be deadly... and manly. Very manly."

Taric.joke03.text: "What did I see upon the mountain? Rocks. Lots of rocks."

Taric.joke04.text: "Much like a fine gem, I'm multifaceted."

Taric.joke05.text: "You know what they say about big gems, right?"

Taric.joke06.text: "My gems aren't merely outrageous, they're fabulous."

Taric.joke07.text: "It's okay if you're impressed. The Protector was too."

Taric.joke08.text: "I'm much more than a pretty face."

Taric.itemSunfireCape01.text: "Wish I'd had this on the mountain."

Taric.itemSunfireCape02.text: "Can never be too warm... or too beautiful."

Taric.itemWarmogsArmor01.text: "You can always use a little extra protection."

Taric.itemTargonsBrace03.text: "I thank the mountain for its gifts."

Yorick_Select_new.text: "Fear not... I will make use of your corpse."

Yorick.start01.text: "I once had honor before the Ruination."

Yorick.start02.text: "This land will never heal. But I will lay it to rest."

Yorick.start03.text: "Tired, ancient, and half-dead. Still, I come for you."

Yorick.start10.text: "I am the rift between life and death. The thin divide between breath and grave."

Yorick.start04.text:
Maiden:    "Yorick, look what you've become."
 Yorick: "I've become what I must be."

Yorick.start05.text:
Maiden:    "Let us in, remove your chains."
 Yorick: "I think not."

Yorick.start06.text:
Maiden:    "Your human form is so confining. You could be infinite."
 Yorick: "I am enough."

Yorick.start07.text:
Maiden:    "There is no hope."
 Yorick: "There is some."

Yorick.start08.text:
Maiden:    "We see you, Yorick. We know your weakness."
 Yorick: "You know nothing."

Yorick.start09.text:
Maiden:    "Join us in eternity, Yorick."
 Yorick: "In the beyond, once you're free."

Yorick.attack01.text: “The hole I dig, it is for you.”

Yorick.attack12.text: "You decay and do not know it."

Yorick.attack15.text: "I will not damn you. I will end you."

Yorick.attackBaron01.text: "That is a lot of flesh to raise."

Yorick.attackBaron02.text: "Even your kind will join the mist."

Yorick.attackDragon01.text: "Your kind is supposed to live long. I am sorry."

Yorick.move01.text: "What I do is just. Every horrid piece of it."

Yorick.move02.text: "The Mist writhes, searching for a place to take root."

Yorick.move04.text: "We're dead much longer than we are alive."

Yorick.move05.text: "What hell is worse than this limbo?"

Yorick.move06.text: "Everyone I knew is dead. How are things with you?"

Yorick.move07.text: "They once called these isles undying. Yet die, they will."

Yorick.move08.text: "How quick the turn from blessed to cursed."

Yorick.move11.text: "The beyond is waiting. Strive to meet it."

Yorick.move12.text: "I am no tyrant. These souls act on their own."

Yorick.move14.text: "The isles were once paradise; now they're a prison."

Yorick.move16.text: "The constant wailing of souls in torment."

Yorick.move17.text: "I cling to life by the thinnest thread."

Yorick.move18.text: "If they could see what I see, they'd long for death."

Yorick.move19.text: "But for the waters, the mist would take me."

Yorick.move20.text: "The Ruined King will soon meet the victims of his curse."

Yorick.move21.text: "From the ground they come, and to it, they return."

Yorick.move22.text: "Ours is a fate worse than death."

Yorick.move23.text: "I carry these souls to their end... wherever it may be."

Yorick.move24.text: "Water for the living, shovel for the dead."

Yorick.move25.text: "Our souls are a small price to pay to cleanse this land."

Yorick.move26.text: "I am the first and last of my order."

Yorick.move28.text: "I remember when I put them in the ground."

Yorick.move30.text: "To most, life is fleeting; to me, it is quagmire."

Yorick.move33.text: "Tell me of the beyond... in case I never make it."

Yorick.move35.text: "The Ruined King's allies shall fall with him."

Yorick.move36.text: "One can stare into the grave too long."

Yorick.move37.text: "This journey is long, but I will complete it."

Yorick.move38.text: "I do not live in hope. I work to return it."

Yorick.move40.text: "Do you hear that? It is the end."

Yorick.move42.text: "Hallowed or profane... I no longer know."

Yorick.move44.text: "It is to the grave, we go."

Yorick.move46.text: "Remember my name. For one day, I will not."

Yorick.move47.text: "I do not know what lies beyond. But it is better than this."

Yorick.move48.text: "The dead don't hear you, no matter how you cry."

Yorick.move49.text: "The dead shall forgive me. I hope."

Yorick.joke01.text: "Ah, missed it. There it goes! Where is it at? - ah! Yes!"

Yorick.jokeAmumu01.text: "Ah, would you like some friends? Nope, can’t have 'em."

Yorick.interactionJokeEnemy01.text: "I suppose I have eternity to think about that one."
Yorick.interactionJokeEnemy01.trigger: When an Enemy Champion Jokes Nearby

Yorick.taunt01.text: "You'll make a fine addition to my cloak."

Yorick.taunt02.text: "For you, I won't dig too deep."

Yorick.tauntMutant01.text: "I pity what you have become. Shall I end your suffering?"

Yorick.tauntEkkoZilean01.text: "I have nothing but time. Show me something else."
Yorick.tauntEkkoZilean01.trigger: Taunting an Enemy Time Traveler ( Ekko / Zilean )

Yorick.tauntYordle01.text: "Yours is an easy grave to dig, small one."

Yorick.tauntChild01.text: "They say I was once your age, though I can't quite recall."

Yorick.tauntAzir01.text: "Your corpses against mine. May the best win."

Yorick.tauntHecarim01.text: "Those you ride down will soon rise against you."

Yorick.tauntKalista01.text: "You and I share a common goal. The similarities end there."

Yorick.tauntKarthus01.text: "Enjoy this limbo while you can, for I will soon end it."

Yorick.tauntKindred01.text: "I know you. And I see you always."

Yorick.tauntKindred02.text: "One day, you will take me. May it be soon."

Yorick.tauntLucian01.text: "No, Lucian, I haven't seen your wife."

Yorick.tauntLux01.text: "You remind me that the world is sometimes good - and very naive."

Yorick.tauntMaokai01.text: "I fight to free you as well - though a hatchet would suffice."

Yorick.tauntMordekaiser01.text: "My army will soon storm your gates, revenant."

Yorick.tauntRyze01.text: "Yours is a fool's errand. The world must be allowed to die."

Yorick.tauntSinged01.text: "You think you want immortality. I'll gladly give you mine."

Yorick.tauntThresh01.text: "Those souls are not yours to keep."

Yorick.interactionTauntEnemy01.text: "I've endured more pain than any words can bring."

Yorick.interactionTauntEnemy02.trigger: When an Enemy Champion Taunts Nearby

Yorick.interactionTauntEnemy03.trigger: When an Enemy Champion Taunts Nearby

Yorick.spellQ7.text: "Some of these faces I know well."

Yorick.spellQ10.text: "Wake up. You have a new task."

Yorick.spellQ11.text: "Die with me brothers, and be free."

Yorick.spellQ14.text: "Welcome back, you won't be here long."

Yorick.spellW3.text: "The ruins of these isles rise to smite you."

Yorick.spellW5.text: "To destroy the curse, I use it."

Yorick.spellR9.text: "We are not corruption. We are strength!"

Yorick.spellR10.text: "More, more for the black maw of the mist!"

Yorick.item01.text: "Don't bury me with it. You can't take it with you."

Yorick.item02.text: "Even a monk needs bread and water."

Yorick.itemRubyCrystal01.text: "It pulses with life, as the isles once did."

Yorick.itemRubyCrystal02.text: "Red is the heart that barely beats in me."

Yorick.itemClothArmor01.text: "I wouldn't be caught dead in that."

Yorick.itemClothArmor03.text: "A sack to cover flesh and bone."

Yorick.itemClothArmor04.text: "The armor of someone soon to die."

Yorick.itemIcebornGauntlet01.text: "As cold as the hand of death."

Yorick.itemSteraksGage01.text: "A gauntlet to throw before the king."

 Yorick: "The sword of a fool."

Yorick.itemBladeOfTheRuinedKing04.text:
Maiden:    "This blade has performed great feats."
 Yorick: "And I will use it to undo them."
Yorick.itemBladeOfTheRuinedKing04.trigger: Upon Buying Blade of the Ruined King

Yorick.itemDeadMansPlate02.text: "Taken from one who can no longer use it."

Yorick.itemDeadMansPlate03.text: "The dead need no armor, but I do."

Yorick.kill01.text: "Another voice in the cacophony of wails."

Yorick.kill04.text:
Maiden:    "Look at the wrong you do!"
 Yorick: "It is necessary."

Yorick.killShadowIsles01.text: "One more nail in the coffin of the isles."

Yorick.recall05.text:

 Yorick: "I will return anon."

Yorick.respawn02.text: "I've come too far to stay dead."

Yorick.respawn03.text: "We do not die, and so we fight on."

Yorick.respawn06.text: "One day, I will no longer awaken."

Yorick.respawn08.text:
Maiden:    "A futile act, why do you persist?"
 Yorick: "Because I must."

Yorick.respawn09.text: "The beyond is not given. It is earned."

Yorick.respawn11.text: "There will be no requiem. Not yet."

Diana.joke1.text: "A man, a woman and a yordle walk into the sun. They die! Because it burns them alive? Heh heh heh heh."

Diana.joke2.text: "Knock, knock. Who's there? The moon... it's far away! You were alone the whole time! Ha ha ha!"

Diana.taunt1.text: "They called me a heretic, now they are dead."

Diana.taunt2.text: "The moon will rise. The night will last forever."

AurelionSol.start01.text: "They call me a comet. They call me a dragon. They have no words for my true form."

AurelionSol.start02.text: "Cower, worship, beg, they're all valid reactions."

AurelionSol.start03.text: "In a constantly shifting cosmos, a world this static is... refreshing."

AurelionSol.start04.text: "There simply are no other dragons like me."

AurelionSol.start06.text: "Hope. Wonder. Insignificance. Imagine what they'll feel when I complete the stars."

AurelionSol.attack03.text: "Let's end this on a high note!"

AurelionSol.attack05.text: "Never stand in the path of a star."

AurelionSol.attack07.text: "It's beyond too late to seek cover."

AurelionSol.attack11.text: "Lighten up, destruction needn't be a maudlin affair."

AurelionSol.attack12.text: "Suns never burn for the benefit of dust."

AurelionSol.attack19.text: "I'm going to throw a star at you now. Good luck."

AurelionSol.attack23.text: "Nothing a little star fire cannot fix."

AurelionSol.attackDragon01.text: "Terrestrial dragons - a study of flawed constitutions."

AurelionSol.attackDragon03.text: "You call yourself a dragon? You're low-flame at best."

AurelionSol.attackDragon04.text: "A dragon that still needs wings to fly? Keep trying, you'll get there."

AurelionSol.attackDragon05.text: "I did mean to call you back, but stars needed forging."

AurelionSol.move01.text: "This world holds the key to Targon's undoing."

AurelionSol.move02.text: "Targon has used me as its weapon for far too long."

AurelionSol.move04.text: "I would burn the cosmos to catch Targon in the flames."

AurelionSol.move05.text: "The depths of space crawl with terrible entities. Pray they ignore this world."

AurelionSol.move06.text: "There are countless colors, but I suppose a single rainbow was a good start."

AurelionSol.move07.text: "This sun is off its axis - it's been driving me crazy for eons now."

AurelionSol.move08.text: "Planetary life... the insufferable byproduct of dim stars."

AurelionSol.move10.text: "Nothing kindles wonder like the beauty of stars."

AurelionSol.move11.text: "Celestial dragons live and die by our own beautiful rules."

AurelionSol.move12.text: "Love is as real a force as gravity. Try it once in a while."

AurelionSol.move13.text: "Stars are not born, they are made... by me."

AurelionSol.move14.text: "A star's birth is as violent as it is breathtaking."

AurelionSol.move15.text: "I've waited millennia to watch Targon fall."

AurelionSol.move16.text: "All beings are made of the same stardust."

AurelionSol.move17.text: "With a few more basic elements I could really make this place shimmer."

AurelionSol.move18.text: "The stars are not to thank for any good luck one may experience."

AurelionSol.move19.text: "This sun could do with a new core."

AurelionSol.move20.text: "Any relevant species has been knocked back into the Stone Age once or twice."

AurelionSol.move21.text: "I wouldn't navigate by the stars. They are a work in progress."

AurelionSol.move22.text: "Each star is one of my hearts."

AurelionSol.move23.text: "My works are revered by worlds I have never even visited."

AurelionSol.move24.text: "Wherever I am is the fashionable part of the universe. Even here."

AurelionSol.move27.text: "A star is so much more than a luminous sphere of wonder."

AurelionSol.move28.text: "If you ask me, we have set the bar too low for sentience."

AurelionSol.move29.text: "My home is in the cosmos, amongst my stars."

AurelionSol.move30.text: "The stories they tell about me? They're probably true."

AurelionSol.move31.text: "All terrestrial dragons are but pale imitations of my kind."

AurelionSol.move32.text: "Perhaps there is more to this world than I thought - not much, but enough."

AurelionSol.move34.text: "Why does anyone wish upon a star?"

AurelionSol.move35.text: "Stars never align for anyone - except me, of course."

AurelionSol.move38.text: "Only when darkness overwhelms the heavens will Targon realise its folly."

AurelionSol.move40.text: "Targon will be the pyre from which I forge a new heaven."

AurelionSol.move41.text: "I see a universe drained of light and heat, where not even a story will survive."

AurelionSol.move42.text: "I grieve for every star never born."

AurelionSol.move44.text: "Whenever I think my work is complete, I end up back here, under this sun."

AurelionSol.moveEnemyBase01.text: "May I enter? Just joking - star dragons don't need permission."

AurelionSol.taunt01.text: "Your demise will be sung about for ages to come - only thanks to its proximity to me, of course."

AurelionSol.taunt02.text: "Your survival is not impossible, only very... very... very unlikely."

AurelionSol.taunt03.text: "I shall be the last thing you see. Lucky you."

AurelionSol.taunt04.text: "Make a wish. See if the stars answer. I'll wait."

AurelionSol.taunt05.text: "What is the definition of underwhelming? Oh, right! You."

AurelionSol.taunt06.text: "I used to wander the stars. Now I'm stuck down here, with you."

AurelionSol.taunt07.text: "On other worlds, there is emerging life more complex than you."

AurelionSol.tauntAhri01.text: "You aspire to be human? Oh, darling, there are so many other variants on mediocrity!"

AurelionSol.tauntAmumu01.text: "I am... overwhelmed by an emotion when you are not around. It is called... happiness."

AurelionSol.tauntAnnie01.text: "Mages are infants grasping at the machinery behind reality. At least you have a plausible excuse."

AurelionSol.tauntAzir01.text: "You Ascended certainly know how to pick an animal totem."

AurelionSol.tauntAzir02.text: "Your immortality is but a grain of sand in time's vast desert."

AurelionSol.tauntBard01.text: "Pick a dimension, Bard, you're confusing them!"

AurelionSol.tauntBard02.text: "Were you born this flat, or did you work at it?"

AurelionSol.tauntCaitlyn01.text: "The funnier the hat, the greater the prestige, right?"

AurelionSol.tauntCelestial01.trigger: Taunting an Enemy with a Celestial Skin

AurelionSol.tauntDiana01.text: "You and Leona embody the same light. Typical Targon redundancy."

AurelionSol.tauntDiana02.text: "It is always a moon's role to envy the stars."

AurelionSol.tauntDragonSlayer01.trigger: Taunting an Enemy with a Dragon Slayer Skin

AurelionSol.tauntDragonTrainerTristana01.text: "Oh, come on, have a little self-respect!"
AurelionSol.tauntDragonTrainerTristana01.trigger: Taunting an Enemy Dragon Trainer Tristana

AurelionSol.tauntDunkmasterDarius01.text: "If dunking is the apex of this primitive sport, then I am the queen of space."

AurelionSol.tauntEkko01.text: "Made a mistake? Better rewind and repeat until you achieve mediocrity."

AurelionSol.tauntHuman01.text: "Ah, mankind. Ever fumbling from one brink of cataclysm to the next."

AurelionSol.tauntHuman02.text: "Humanity, surprisingly adept in the art of wrestling survival from the clutches of extinction."

AurelionSol.tauntHuman03.text: "As far as fauna goes, humans strike a firm... middle."

AurelionSol.tauntIllaoi02.text: "I've seen the main act. You're only a third-rate cover band."

AurelionSol.tauntIllaoi01.text: "You do not understand your god, Illaoi."

AurelionSol.tauntJhin.text: "Imagine what you could do with a larger canvas."

AurelionSol.tauntJinx01.text: "Life is short, go crazy once in a while, I get it."

AurelionSol.tauntLeona02.text: "You and Diana embody the same light. Typical Targon redundancy."

AurelionSol.tauntMalphite01.text: "There is a saying on this planet - "Dumb as a rock". It's not a compliment."

AurelionSol.tauntMissFortune01.text: "You are going to kill me? Dressed like that?"

AurelionSol.tauntNasus01.text: "Bravo, Nasus, you've ascended yourself into a dog! Now fetch me something more interesting."

AurelionSol.tauntNasus02.text: "I could teach an old dog millions of new tricks, but I simply don't like you, Nasus."

AurelionSol.tauntPantheon01.text: "Your fate was sealed the moment you picked up Targon's spear."

AurelionSol.tauntRammus01.text: "Are you burdened by your own monotony? Because I am."

AurelionSol.tauntRenekton01.text: "That whole practice of Ascension is adorably amusing, like a kitten trying to walk upright."

AurelionSol.tauntRyze01.text: "Ah, Ryze, I see you've brought paper to take notes."

AurelionSol.tauntRyze02.text: "True magic is beyond language. Writing merely butchers the intent."

AurelionSol.tauntRyze03.text: "Magic tattoos? Where did you get those, magic prison?... oh."

AurelionSol.tauntShyvana02.text: "A dragon's loyalty is a priceless gift. Do not waste it in the service of fools."

AurelionSol.tauntShyvana03.text: "Medium flame, and that is me being generous."

AurelionSol.tauntSoraka01.text: "Twinkle, twinkle, little star, do you wonder what you are?"

AurelionSol.tauntTahmKench01.text: "The heavens drag on endlessly... much like a conversation with you."

AurelionSol.tauntTargon01.text: "The Aspect of Targon? Sparks masquerading as lightning."

AurelionSol.tauntTargon02.text: "I will cauterize Targon with star fire."

AurelionSol.tauntTaric01.text: "You're an Aspect? Let me guess - tackiness."

AurelionSol.tauntTryndamere01.text: "Galaxies exist by my will - but, yes, that is certainly an impressive sword."

AurelionSol.tauntVi02.text: "You are going to punch a star dragon. Good luck with that."

AurelionSol.tauntZac01.text: "I empathize with your life as a weapon, but have a little backbone."

AurelionSol.tauntZilean01.text: "You bend time the way a child folds origami - cute, but nothing special."

AurelionSol.joke01.text: "Few can impress me. That is a compliment."

AurelionSol.joke02.text: "Which star is your favorite? I made that one."

AurelionSol.joke03.text: "I made the stars... but you inspire me to make more."

AurelionSol.joke04.text: "First you start with some matter, then add star fire and voila! It basically does the rest itself."

AurelionSol.joke05.text: "Runeterra? I mean the name of this world literally means 'magic earth'."

AurelionSol.joke06.text: "I made the stars to illuminate the perpetual nothing, and mortals use them for... relationship advice."

AurelionSol.joke07.text: "A sun is unimaginable celestial power - and thrilled mortals use theirs to coordinate this 'lunch time'."

AurelionSol.joke09.text: "Of course I love Runeterra! You have buildings and... more buildings."

AurelionSol.dance01.text: "Hello, Runeterra! Are you ready to rock?"

AurelionSol.item01.text: "Put it on my tab. The name's Pantheon, with a P."

AurelionSol.item03.text: "Pay? Do you know who I am?"

AurelionSol.itemRodofAges01.text: "Some things are simply better with age."

AurelionSol.itemRodofAges02.text: "Ages? This thing has been around for centuries, tops."

AurelionSol.itemRodofAges03.text: "It's been around for ages? So... almost new."

AurelionSol.itemRodofAges04.text: "All things appreciate in value over time."

AurelionSol.itemRabadonsDeathcap02.text: "As long as it's set at a jaunty angle I'm in."

AurelionSol.itemOrbofWinter01.text: "A snow globe? Perfect for my collect - to destroy you. Destroy you!"

AurelionSol.itemRylaisCrystalScepter01.text: "Time to slow things down a bit."

AurelionSol.itemRylaisCrystalScepter02.text: "A bit gaudy for my tastes but exceedingly useful."

AurelionSol.itemLiandrysTorment02.text: "Perfect for the bimillenial celestial masquerade ball."

AurelionSol.itemLiandrysTorment03.text: "If Bard and Kindred can pull off wearing a mask, so can I."

AurelionSol.itemLudensEcho01.text: "There are no echoes where I'm from."

AurelionSol.tower01.text: "All towers fall - it's just what they do when I'm around."
AurelionSol.tower01.trigger: Upon an Enemy Turret Dropping Below 30% Health

AurelionSol.tower02.text: "Nothing they build can endure like the celestial firmament."
AurelionSol.tower02.trigger: Upon an Enemy Turret Dropping Below 30% Health

AurelionSol.tower03.text: "Towers tend to crumble when I am in the vicinity."
AurelionSol.tower03.trigger: Upon an Enemy Turret Dropping Below 30% Health

AurelionSol.tower04.text: "Topple, like all things crafted by mortals."
AurelionSol.tower04.trigger: Upon an Enemy Turret Dropping Below 30% Health

AurelionSol.tower05.text: "The architects of these towers misunderstand object permanence."
AurelionSol.tower05.trigger: Upon an Enemy Turret Dropping Below 30% Health

AurelionSol.towerKill01.text: "How many must I knock down before they learn?"

AurelionSol.firstblood01.text: "You may look forward to more of this."

AurelionSol.ace01.text: "Never stop when you're on a roll."

AurelionSol.ace02.text: "I shall inscribe this moment in the stars."

AurelionSol.pentakill01.text: "That ought to keep them talking for the next century or so."

AurelionSol.pentakill02.text: "Cosmic dragon; five. Everyone else; zero. Please, take notes."

AurelionSol.recall04.text: "Always know when to make an entrance - and an exit."

AurelionSol.death01.text: "Alas, I am simply too beautiful for this world."

AurelionSol.death04.text: "The brightest stars shine on long after they're gone."

AurelionSol.deathShyvana01.text: "Darling, you have but set my hearts free."
AurelionSol.deathShyvana01.trigger: Upon Being Killed by an Enemy Shyvana

AurelionSol.shutdown01.text: "With a lifespan as comically brief as yours, I suppose I can allow you to taste triumph at least once."

AurelionSol.shutdown02.text: "Ah, the joys of lesser organisms rising up to slay their betters! If only they were aware of the impermanence of being... or the permanence of me."

AurelionSol.respawn02.text: "Because I am a star dragon. That's why."

AurelionSol.respawn03.text: "It's not a comeback if one was never truly gone."

Kayn: "Will you prove worthy?"

Kayn_Ban.text:
Kayn: "The weak fear the shadows."
 Rhaast: "Fear controls them."

Kayn.start1.text: Rhaast: "I will survive eternity. They will die today!"

Kayn.start2.text: Kayn: "The child is gone, the killer will remain."

Kayn.start3.text:
Rhaast: "There is fear in your grip, and doubt in your heart!"
 Kayn: "I have no heart. That, you should fear."

Kayn.start4.text:
Kayn: "The true assassin kills one to save many"
 Rhaast: "Such noble lies. Save no-one, it's so liberating!"

Kayn.start5.text:
Rhaast: "The undoing draws near."
 Kayn: "Yes, yours."

Kayn.attack03.text:
Rhaast: "They are worthy?"
 Kayn: "To die? Yes."

Kayn.attack07.text: Kayn: "Cowering in the light, how foolish!"

Kayn.attack15.text: Rhaast: "From the shadow comes the slaughter."

Kayn.attackAatrox.text:
Kayn: "He's with you I assume?"
 Rhaast: "Aatrox ... we have ... history..."

Kayn.attackZed1.text:
Rhaast: "This is your master? Zed?"
 Kayn: "Leave us to it!"

Kayn.attackShen01.text:
Kayn: "This brings me no pleasure, Shen."
 Rhaast: "It will for me."

Kayn.attackDragon.text:
Kayn: "The bigger they are..."
 Rhaast: "The louder they scream."

Kayn.attackRiftScuttler2.text: Kayn: "This will only dull the blade."

Kayn.move1.text:
Rhaast: "There is much darkness around you, in you."
 Kayn: "That is my armor."

Kayn.move2.text:
Kayn: "I let you go and you will die."
 "Rhaast: And you will lose."

Kayn.move3.text:
Rhaast: "Tell me, was it desperation that led you to me?"
 Kayn: "Audacity."

Kayn.move4.text:
Kayn: "I am the weapon, you are a tool."
 Rhaast: "Lies sooth the mind, don't they?"

Kayn.move5.text:
Rhaast: "I see your nightmares, do they trouble you?"
 Kayn: "Not nightmares, plans..."

Kayn.move6.text:
Rhaast: "I have waited eons to bathe this realm in blood!"
 Kayn: "Talk, talk... You'll do nothing without me."

Kayn.move7.text:
Rhaast: "Ionians, are they all as confident as you?"
 Kayn: "There is no one like me."

Kayn.move8.text:
Kayn: "What will be the final lesson?"
 Rhaast: "Give in, and I will show you."

Kayn.move9.text: Kayn: "I was born into a nation of despair and I alone am the remedy."

Kayn.move10.text: Kayn: "I have chosen you, you will serve me."

Kayn.move11.text: Kayn: "I have mastered every weapon of war, no prattling tool will prove an exception."

Kayn.move12.text: Kayn: "Who should I obey? Master Zed or the farm implement with delusions of grandure?"

Kayn.move14.text: Rhaast: "The rage is in your hands, let it loose!"

Kayn.move16.text: Rhaast: "Zed's order shackles you, I offer freedom!"

Kayn.move17.text: Rhaast: "You are not worthy of the power you hold."

Kayn.move18.text: Rhaast: "This is the part I like best, the anticipation. No, it's the killing."

Kayn.move19.text: Rhaast: "Such an obsequious pupil, I will be your new master."

Kayn.move20.text: Rhaast: "Target the strong, I am a weapon not some accessory."

Kayn.move21.text: Rhaast: "Neither time nor violence will end me."

Kayn.move22.text:
Kayn: "What does Rhaast mean anyway?"
 Rhaast: "Obey."

Kayn.move25.text:
Kayn: "I learned from a young age to embrace the shadows."
 Rhaast: "Darkness is a start."

Kayn.move26.text:
Rhaast: "I am no toy Kayn."
 Kayn: "You possess the hubris of a more fearsome weapon."

Kayn.move27.text: Kayn: "(Laughs) Their screams will echo in this place"

Kayn.move31.text: Rhaast: "Stain this fetid swamp with their blood."

Kayn.move32.text:
Rhaast: "Oh how I miss the smell of blood in the water"
 Kayn: "Today you will be reminded."

Kayn.move33.text: Kayn: "Wait by the river long enough and the enemy dead will float by"

Kayn.move34.text: Rhaast: "Oh yeah... Let's turn this river red."

Kayn.firstMove01.text:
Kayn: "The blood of the fallen will annoint me the new master."
Rhaast:"Everyone does look better in red."

Kayn.firstMove02.text:
Rhaast: "Rage inside me will not be contained!"
Kayn: "The spade does not dictate the architect's vision."
Kayn.firstMove02.trigger: Upon Moving for the First Time

Kayn.firstMove03.text:
Kayn: "Lives will be taken, and the real plan revealed"
Rhaast: "Killing is the plan, let me show you."

Rhaast: "Such noble lies, save no one; It's so liberating!"

Kayn.killAatrox02.text: Rhaast: "Your skills have not improved, Aatrox."

Kayn.killZed01.text: Rhaast: "Zed is dead baby, Zed is dead."

Kayn.killZed02.text: Kayn: "It should not have come to this, Zed."

Kayn.killZed03.text: Kayn: "You taught me too well master."

Kayn.killZed04.text: Kayn: "Live by the shadow, die by the shadow."

Kayn.killZed05.text: Rhaast: "Zed's final lesson? Don't be him."

Kayn.killShen01.text: Kayn: "Shen, consider this a debt paid to a friend"

Kayn.penta01.text: Kayn: "You wanted mercy? Not from me!"

Kayn.taunt01.text: Kayn: "There are a thousand ways to kill you in this moment, I'm planning the right one."

Kayn.taunt02.text: Kayn: "This will be quick, but still painful."

Kayn.taunt03.text: Rhaast: "I was forged to destroy, and you are in my way."

Kayn.taunt04.text: Rhaast: "I will take that pitiful existence you call a life from you."

Kayn.tauntAllyAatrox.text: Rhaast: "Death and war, this will be delicious."

Kayn.tauntAllyVarus.text: Rhaast: "We find Aatrox... and it's a party. Of murder. A murder party!"

Kayn.joke01.text: Rhaast: "I find your will to live... Amusing.."

Kayn.joke02.text: Kayn: "I can see twelve ways to kill you. Ah! Correction! Thirteen. It's thirteen.

Kayn.joke03.text: Kayn: "I'm holding a sentient weapon of doom, denied blood for eons. You think I am scared of you?"

Kayn.joke04.text: Rhaast: "I smell death... no, it's you. You smell... bad."

Kayn.joke05.text:
Rhaast: "A craftsman never blames his tools."
Kayn: "I will make an exception in this case."

Kayn.castE02.text:

Rhaast: "Oh. I do like this"

Kayn.castR01.text: Kayn: "Hu hu ha ha ha ha."

 Kayn: "Do not question me, or my motives."

Kayn.recall2.text:
Rhaast: "The weak run. Stay and fight!"
 Kayn: "Did such foolishness lead to your imprisonment?"

Kayn.recall4.text: Rhaast: "But there's still so much to kill!"

Kayn.placeWard01.text: Kayn: "For those who can not see in the dark."

Kayn.placeWard03.text: Rhaast: "Done. Now can we continue the bloodbath?"

Kayn.destroyWard01.text: Kayn: "Sight.. A pitiful crutch for the weak."

Kayn.purchase02.text: Rhaast: "Well.. You know what you want."

Kayn.purchase03.text: Rhaast: "Not my first choice, but okay."

Kayn.purchase05.text: Kayn: "This will very much upset the balance"

Kayn.purchase07.text: Rhaast: "Good choice, pairs nicely with wrath and fury."

Taliyah.attack02.text: "Our paths have woven together for a reason."

Taliyah.attack06.text: "Mastery is a journey. Here's your first lesson."

Taliyah.attack07.text: "Okay, great, that is actually what I wanted to have happen. For once."

Taliyah.attack08.text: "My father always said I was a shepherd's nightmare."

Taliyah.attack09.text: "It will take more than you to break me."

Taliyah.attack20.text: "A rock in my hand is worth two in your face!"

Taliyah.attack24.text: "Either way, I'm going to learn something from this."

Taliyah.attack25.text: "Looks like you've got a thing or two to learn yourself."

Taliyah.attack29.text: "Every rock tells a story. This one might be painful."

Taliyah.attack36.text: "I am the stone beneath your feet."

Taliyah.attack38.text: "The best defense is a strong foundation."

Taliyah.attackBaron02.text: "As before, we will stand against you."

Taliyah.attackDragon01.text: "Your fire is nothing compared to the desert heat."

Taliyah.attackDragon02.text: "I looked for your kind at the ends of the earth."

Taliyah.attackVilemaw02.text: "My weave is made of sturdier stuff."

Taliyah.move04.text: "The great Weaver says every lesson is a gift."

Taliyah.move07.text: "The desert's beauty lies beneath the sand."

Taliyah.move09.text: "Keep your eyes on the horizon and your feet on the ground."

Taliyah.move10.text: "My journey is not yet at an end."

Taliyah.move11.text: "A tribe without tradition is a flock without a shepherd."

Taliyah.move12.text: "It is up to all of us to see beauty in the bare stone."

Taliyah.move13.text: "Distance means so little when family means so much."

Taliyah.move14.text: "The earth calls, and I must answer."

Taliyah.move15.text: "To conquer our fears, we must move forward."

Taliyah.move16.text: "So long as the desert blooms, there is hope."

Taliyah.move19.text: "True learning is just a stone's throw away."

Taliyah.move20.text: "Oh, look, a rock... and another... and another!"

Taliyah.move21.text: "I know all of this will lead me home someday."

Taliyah.move23.text: "This world is a tapestry of our own making."

Taliyah.move27.text: "I keep moving, but my feet are on solid ground."

Taliyah.move28.text: "If I stumble, I have the earth to catch me."

Taliyah.move29.text: "The world is my loom, and every stone my thread."

Taliyah.move30.text: "This world is frayed, and in need of mending."

Taliyah.move32.text: "I think I've learned what I need to here."

Taliyah.move33.text: "I must push myself harder next time."

Taliyah.move34.text: "The warmth of the desert calls me home."

Taliyah.moveIdle01.text: "Just when I start to appreciate the view, it is time to move on."
Taliyah.moveIdle01.trigger: Upon Moving After Speaking an Idle Phrase

Taliyah.taunt01.text: "Maybe I'm here to teach you something."

Taliyah.taunt02.text: "You're never too old to learn something new."

Taliyah.taunt03.text: "Go ahead, push me. We'll both find out what I'm made of."

Taliyah.taunt04.text: "You're not a problem, you're a learning opportunity."

Taliyah.tauntIonian01.text: (Ally) "The mountains of Ionia taught me much."

Taliyah.tauntJhin01.text: "You're no artist, just a hired gun!"

Taliyah.tauntJhin02.text: "Beauty is no excuse for so much suffering."

Taliyah.tauntYasuo03.text: "I've learned much since we last met."

Taliyah.tauntYasuo04.text: "Let me show you what I've learned."

Taliyah.tauntNoxian01.text: "The promises of Noxus are nothing but lies."

Taliyah.tauntNoxian02.text: "I will take no part in your war machine."

Taliyah.tauntNoxian03.text: "You are nothing but plunderers and poachers."

Taliyah.tauntNoxian04.text: "We will not trade the yoke of one empire for another."

Taliyah.tauntNoxian05.text: "The earth will rip itself apart before it falls to Noxus."

Taliyah.tauntNoxian06.text: "Noxus promised learning, but delivered only bloodshed."

Taliyah.tauntCassiopeia01.text: "The sands have revealed your true form."

Taliyah.tauntCassiopeia03.text: "This is how the desert repays thieves."

Taliyah.tauntCassiopeia04.text: "Noxians... why did it have to be Noxians?"

Taliyah.tauntChoGath01.text: "You are the scourge upon our world."

Taliyah.tauntKassadin02.text: "Tell us what we need to stand against those creatures."

Taliyah.tauntMalzahar01.text: "You have betrayed our people to chaos."

Taliyah.tauntMalzahar02.text: "The stone of Shurima will stand against those creatures."

Taliyah.tauntRekSai01.text: "You will stalk the sands no more."

Taliyah.tauntRekSai02.text: "You breed chaos like a rabid ralsiji!"

Taliyah.tauntVelKoz02.text: "Want to examine some stone up close?"

Taliyah.tauntVelKoz03.text: "How's that for dirt in your eye?"

Taliyah.tauntAnnie01.text: "Playtime is going to get a little rocky."

Taliyah.tauntAurelionSol01.text: "Even the smallest stone can shake the heavens."

Taliyah.tauntAzir01.text: "Remember there is stone beneath your sand."

Taliyah.tauntAzir04.text: "There is no empire without the people."

Taliyah.tauntAzir05.text: "Close to the ground, the sparrow flies faster than the falcon."

Taliyah.tauntAzir07.text: "Better to build on stone than sand."

Taliyah.tauntAzir09.text: "Shouldn't you be home polishing your Sun Disc?"

Taliyah.tauntEkko01.text: "Did the earth move for you too? Did I just say that out loud?"

Taliyah.tauntIllaoi01.text: "Don't worry. I don't stay in one place for long."

Taliyah.tauntKindred01.text: "Life and death are two ends of the same thread."

Taliyah.tauntMalphite03.text: (Enemy) "Even rock gives under the right pressure."

Taliyah.tauntNasus01.text: "Our future is not yet off the loom."

Taliyah.tauntNasus02.text: "Worry is a heavier burden than stone."

Taliyah.tauntNasus03.text: "Do not give up before the journey is finished."

Taliyah.tauntNasus04.text: "Even the most barren desert blooms in time."

Taliyah.tauntRenekton02.text: "Stone sealed your tomb once. It will again."

Taliyah.tauntRenekton03.text: "I will mend what you have sundered."

Taliyah.tauntSivir01.text: "He may be your blood, but we are your people."

Taliyah.tauntSivir03.text: "Do not turn your back on what is right."

Taliyah.tauntSkarner01.text: "I feel your tribe sleeping below the earth."

Taliyah.tauntSkarner02.text: "Is it hard to be the protector of so many?"

Taliyah.tauntSkarner03.text: "I know the power that lies beneath."

Taliyah.tauntTaric01.text: "Ooh, you're pretty. Guys can be pretty, right?"

Taliyah.tauntWarwick01.text: "It is the shepherd's duty to drive the wolf away."

Taliyah.tauntWarwick02.text: "You are nothing but a sheep in wolf's clothes."

Taliyah.tauntXerath01.text: "Yours is the ill wind that begat his wrath."

Taliyah.interactionJokeEnemy01.text: (Enemy) "Huh. I guess that's funny where you come from."

Taliyah.spellQ1.text: "Problems should be broken up into little pieces."

Taliyah.spellQ4.text: "If at first you don't succeed, throw another rock!"

Taliyah.spellE1.text: "It's never good to run from your problems."

Taliyah.spellR1.text: "Better to build from the ground up."

Taliyah.spellR7.text: "You can run from a landslide, I prefer to ride it!"

Taliyah.spellR10.text: "That may have gotten away from me."

Taliyah.item08.text: "Learning is always faster with the right tools."

Taliyah.itemBootsBasic01.text: "Every girl needs a good pair of boots."

Taliyah.itemBootsLucidity01.trigger: Upon Buying Ionian Boots of Lucidity

Taliyah.itemVisionWard02.text: "This should make the pattern easier to follow."

Taliyah.itemVisionWard03.text: "Time to see the pattern in the weave."

Taliyah.itemVisionWard04.text: "A rock in the bush is worth five in the hand."

Taliyah.itemRylaisCrystalScepter01.text: "Diamonds really are a girl's best friend."

Taliyah.itemAncientCoin01.text: "This currency carries weight beyond the sands."

Taliyah.itemEyeOfTheOasis01.text: "A vision most welcome in the sands."
Taliyah.itemEyeOfTheOasis01.trigger: Upon Buying Eye of the Oasis

Taliyah.itemRabadonsDeathcap01.text: "Let's see what I can pull out of this hat."

Taliyah.itemTearOfTheGoddess01.trigger: Upon Buying Tear of the Goddess

Taliyah.itemMejaisSoulstealer01.text: "Time to go big or go home."

Taliyah.itemMorellonomicon01.text: "Time to throw the book at them too."

Taliyah.itemAbyssalMask01.text: "Time to fight magic with more magic."

Taliyah.itemHextechProtobelt01.text: "Rocks should really come with an instruction manual."

Taliyah.itemVoidStaff01.text: "A little chaos should shake things up."

Taliyah.shopClose01.text: "Choices. Those are my only true possessions."

Taliyah.interactionTimeMidGame01.text: "The midday toil is the most difficult."

Taliyah.interactionTimeLateGame01.text: "Evening is upon us. Let us finish this."

Taliyah.ward01.text: "Clear vision is best when there are many paths."

Taliyah.ward04.text: "Big dreams require a lot of vision."

Taliyah.ward05.text: "Girls with dreams become women with vision."

Taliyah.ward06.text: "You cannot be what you cannot envision."

Camille_Select.text: "Precision is the difference between a butcher and a surgeon."

Camille_Ban.text: "I will wait for you to be better."

Braum.start01.text: "Good times, good friends... what could be better?"

Braum.start02.text: "If they insist on a fight, I will oblige them."

Braum.start03.text: "Ah! We are about to begin the fighting!"

Braum.start04.text: "Now, what can we learn from fighting?"

Braum.start11.text: "They may have many, but you have me."

Braum.attack01.text: "Why not enjoy some warm milk instead?"

Braum.attack05.text: "When going gets tough, you call Braum."

Braum.attack08.text: "You hit like baby ram! No horns yet!"

Braum.attack09.text: "Now I give more than harsh talking to!"

Braum.attack17.text: "Today we fight each other. Tomorrow, we may fight together."

Braum.move01.text: "Sometimes icy heart just needs warm smile."

Braum.move07.text: "If you have problem, you come to me first."

Braum.move09.text: "The darker the night, the brighter the stars."

Braum.taunt01.text: "If at first you do not succeed, please, tell me what it is like."

Braum.taunt02.text: "Don't worry, Braum was trying little bit."

Braum.tauntAlistar01.text: "You remind me of Agatha. Best cow back home."

Braum.tauntAlistar02.text: "Alistar! I have cow you should meet."

Braum.tauntAnnie01.text: "Mother gave me bear as child too, Annie."

Braum.tauntGragas01.text: "After this, we share a drink! You like goat's milk?"

Braum.tauntVi01.text: "Your hair... we do not see things like this in the Freljord."
Braum.tauntVi01.trigger: Taunting an Enemy Jinx or Vi

Braum.joke01.text: "When life gives you curdled milk, be patient. You get very good cheese!"

Braum.joke02.text: "The goats are wise; eat everything, climb everything, and if something kicks you, kick it back!"

Braum.joke03.text: "Mother always said - float like iceberg, sting like thrown iceberg!"

Braum.caitlyzreal01.text: "Good shot! You'll get them next time."
Braum.caitlyzreal01.trigger: Upon Blocking Ace in the Hole or Trueshot Barrage

Braum.poro02.text: "Train hard, little poro, and one day you will be strong like... baby!"

Braum.coin01.text: "This has the smell of a faraway land. Perhaps I shall see it one day."

Braum.sightstone01.text: "No sneaking up on Braum this time."

Braum.sightstone02.text: "Sight is the key to victory. Also stone."

Braum.frozenHeart01.text: "To friends, I am snowfall. To enemies, I am avalanche!"

Braum.randuins01.trigger: Randuin's Omen or Aegis of the Legion

Braum.randuins02.text: "A shield for my shield? I like it!"
Braum.randuins02.trigger: Randuin's Omen or Aegis of the Legion

Braum.return03.text: "Is very important to take time to rest."

Jhin.start03.text: "I suppose I must make do with this tawdry setting."

Jhin.start04.text: "This stage is beneath my talent, but I shall elevate it."

Jhin.start05.text: "I will bring them an opera of death."

Jhin.attack05.text: "Your life had no value before me."

Jhin.attack29.text: "When they find you, they will cry."

Jhin.attack37.text: "There is no drama in a peaceful death!"

Jhin.move03.text: "The end is important in all things."

Jhin.move05.text: "I must wait until a composition is perfect."

Jhin.move06.text: "They're puppets. I pull their strings, and then they dance."

Jhin.move09.text: "They call me mad. All artists are mad."

Jhin.move11.text: "I cannot be good. I must be perfection."

Jhin.move15.text: "It's so difficult to work under these conditions."

Jhin.move17.text: "I am at my best only during the performance."

Jhin.move18.text: "I am pure. My work is pure."

Jhin.move21.text: "No poet's words could match my craft."

Jhin.move22.text: "Death should never be quick. It should be an opera."

Jhin.move25.text: "The world is cruel. It does not have to be ugly."

Jhin.move26.text: "Everyone wears a mask. I just chose to create my own."

Jhin.move27.text: "This art is a compulsion. I cannot resist it."

Jhin.move30.text: "There is nothing for me but this."

Jhin.move31.text: "I never hurt anyone. It is the performance that kills."

Jhin.move32.text: "Until they stop me, I will keep going."

Jhin.move33.text: "I am the singer without a voice. The dancer without legs."

Jhin.move34.text: "Only to the audience do I show my true face."

Jhin.move35.text: "Each bullet is a piece of my soul. Each shot is a piece of me."

Jhin.move36.text: "I swear each performance is the last, but I lie every time."

Jhin.move37.text: "I am a slave to this passion."

Jhin.move38.text: "My work asks questions, it never has answers."

Jhin.move39.text: "Which is the lie? The mask, or my face?"

Jhin.move40.text: "An icon doesn't have to explain himself."

Jhin.move41.text: "I wonder what they think when they see me."

Jhin.move44.text: "This would be easier if blood came in more colours."

Jhin.move48.text: "If I keep getting interrupted, how can I be expected to work?"

Jhin.move49.text: "I was paid to put on a killer show."

Jhin.move51.text: "They will dance, they will sing, they will die!"

Jhin.move52.text: "A costume, some makeup, a spray of blood."

Jhin.move53.text: "It's very simple - when I shoot, they dance."

Jhin.move55.text: "If I get this outfit dirty, I'm going to be so annoyed."

Jhin.move57.text: "Death is certain, but killing doesn't have to be ugly."

Jhin.move58.text: "I provide catharsis for my clients, and my victims."

Jhin.move60.text: "I get nervous before every performance, but I need that feeling."

Jhin.move61.text: "The moment before the shot... is painful."

Jhin.move62.text: "It is only when the gun fires that I am alive."

Jhin.move64.text: "The trigger on a loaded weapon... it whispers for us to act."

Jhin.move65.text: "I can't live without the euphoria of performance."

Jhin.move67.text: "I want to feel everything. The gun makes it so I do."

Jhin.move68.text: "I envy silence... because I must be loud."

Jhin.taunt03.text: "Killing you will be one of my finest works."

Jhin.taunt04.text: "You are mediocrity. My genius will supplant you."

Jhin.taunt05.text: "Only my actions will make you memorable."

Jhin.tauntIonian01.text: "You only understand harmony. Discord is required for contrast."

Jhin.tauntIonian02.text: "My dear countryman, you remind me how little our culture has advanced."

Jhin.tauntIonian03.text: "I am avant-garde - you are stuck in the past."

Jhin.tauntIonian04.text: "The Noxian invasion should be a wake-up call. We need more elaborate productions."

Jhin.tauntIonian05.text: "I do what others will not. That alone is innovation."

Jhin.tauntShen01.text: "I remember your father! He thought he could censor me."

Jhin.tauntShen02.text: "I have been planning your final performance for a very... long... time."

Jhin.tauntShen03.text: "You helped lock me away. You tried to stop my work. My art cannot be contained."

Jhin.tauntShen04.text: "Your father was a merciful man. Only his failure will be remembered."

Jhin.tauntShen05.text: "Your father's death denied me a performance. You will be his stand-in."

Jhin.tauntZed01.text: "You wanted to kill me back then, didn't you? You will learn - art cannot be killed."

Jhin.tauntZed02.text: "You think you can stop my performance?"

Jhin.tauntZed04.text: "I remember your master. He was worth remembering."

Jhin.tauntZed05.text: "You were wrong to kill your master. I needed him for this performance."

Jhin.tauntZed06.text: "You belong in the shadows. No audience could love you."

Jhin.tauntZed07.text: "I offer an exclusive service. You'll find I murder the competition."

Jhin.tauntNoxian01.text: "I've been asked to do so many boring performances in your nation."

Jhin.tauntNoxian03.text: "Noxians treat killing as a sport. It is an art."

Jhin.tauntNoxian05.text: "Your war was an impressive production, but it lacked soul."

Jhin.tauntDraven01.text: "You shout and throw machetes? How quaint."

Jhin.tauntDraven03.text: "I find your work very, very... obvious."

Jhin.tauntBard01.text: "Wait for your cue! You're only here to herald my entrance."

Jhin.tauntIllaoi01.text: "When you speak, I don't hear god, I hear an idiot babbling."

Jhin.tauntIllaoi02.text: "Here's the thing, I don't need your god, I need more time for my production."

Jhin.tauntIllaoi03.text: "You can take my soul... if you'll shut up."

Jhin.tauntIllaoi04.text: "There is such a thing as 'too much gold', my dear."

Jhin.tauntIllaoi05.text: "I thought diamonds were a girl's best friend."

Jhin.tauntJinx01.text: "So many guns, all lacking in meaning or artistry."

Jhin.tauntLucian01.text: "Your story is revenge with guns and ghosts. How droll."

Jhin.tauntRekSai01.text: "I suppose you embody a primitive minimalism, but you lack my technique."

Jhin.tauntSion01.text: "Break a leg! Hehe, oh. 'Break a leg', hehe... ah, delightful. I do cut myself up."

Jhin.tauntSona01.text: "Your music lacks the cruelty of a masterpiece."

Jhin.tauntSona02.text: "You should learn the power of silence."

Jhin.tauntSona03.text: "Step out of my light! They call it background music!"

Jhin.tauntSona04.text: "Your work will be forgotten. I am ahead of my time!"

Jhin.tauntTahmKench01.text: "How inelegant your words are. Surely a fool wrote your script."

Jhin.tauntTahmKench03.text: "Why would anyone listen to a creature so ugly?"

Jhin.tauntTahmKench04.text: "Heh... hehe... that hat is ridiculous, now... who let you wear that horrible thing?"

Jhin.tauntTahmKench05.text: "Oh, before you ask, yes, your whole ensemble makes you look fat. Very fat."

Jhin.joke01.text: "Only perfectio - gah! ... only perfection is acceptable."

Jhin.I11.text: "You will learn what beauty truly is."
Jhin.I11.trigger: While Whisper's Fourth Shot is Loaded

Jhin.I12.trigger: While Whisper's Fourth Shot is Loaded

Jhin.I13.trigger: While Whisper's Fourth Shot is Loaded

Jhin.I14.trigger: While Whisper's Fourth Shot is Loaded

Jhin.I15.text: "Bliss comes only in the moment before I fire."

Jhin.I16.trigger: While Whisper's Fourth Shot is Loaded

Jhin.E1.text: "Now that is what I want to see."
Jhin.E1.trigger: When a Champion Steps on a Lotus Trap

Jhin.E2.trigger: When a Champion Steps on a Lotus Trap

Jhin.E3.text: "Life has no meaning, but your death shall."
Jhin.E3.trigger: When a Champion Steps on a Lotus Trap

Jhin.E4.text: "I live for the applause, you will die for it."
Jhin.E4.trigger: When a Champion Steps on a Lotus Trap

Jhin.E5.text: "I knew you would find your mark, eventually."
Jhin.E5.trigger: When a Champion Steps on a Lotus Trap

Jhin.E6.trigger: When a Champion Steps on a Lotus Trap

Jhin.E7.text: "Face the crowd, and bleed for them."

Jhin.itemBansheesVeil01.text: "I love to perform, but I hate crowds."

Jhin.itemBerserkersGreaves01.text: "These were clearly designed by a caveman."

Jhin.itemEssenceReaver01.text: "The essence of a thing is found only in its absence."

Jhin.itemHauntingGuise01.text: "We all wear masks. Mine are just better-crafted."

Jhin.itemLastWhisper02.text: "I prefer my equipment to make a bang."

Jhin.itemLiandrysTorment01.text: "Not sure I needed another mask, but oh well."

Jhin.itemPhantomDancer01.text: "Start the music. I will make them dance."

Jhin.itemRapidFirecannon01.text: "Rapid fire? Huh. Where's the drama in that?"

Jhin.itemRunaansHurricane01.text: "The storm is in their hearts. I calm them."

Jhin.itemStatikkShiv01.text: "It is by my will alone I set my mind in motion."

Jhin.itemStatikkShiv02.text: "I do prefer my work to have a brisk tempo."

Jhin.move69.text: "In carnage, I bloom, like a flower in the dawn."

Jhin.move70.text: "I have risen from the filth and muck. I am the lotus blossom. I am beauty."

Jhin.move71.text: "That delightful moment before the curtain goes up."
