Kled_Select.text: "I find courage unpredictable, it's total insanity you can rely on!"

Kled_Ban.text: "Oh, I knew you was all yeller!"

Kled.start01.text:
"Them's humans!"
 Skaarl growls
    "Naw, they're good eatin'."

Kled.start03.text: "What was that? Oh, I should go for the decakill? Uh, if you say so."

Kled.start04.text: "It's my property! All sixty gazillion acres of it!"

Kled.start05.text:
"Holy $%!#, where are we?"
 Skaarl growls
    "Guess we'll have to kill our way out!"

Kled.attackMount01.text: "Slow down so I can kill something!"

Kled.attackMount06.text: "Step on my land again, you're done!"

Kled.attackMount07.text: "How about a long axe in your guts?"

Kled.attackMount09.text: "You should run! Skaarl likes his food lively!"

Kled.attackMount10.text: "Don't interrupt me! I'm trying to start a fight!"

Kled.attackMount12.text: "I'm Kled, and this here's Skaarl. Prepare to die."

Kled.attackMount13.text: "This is how it's gonna work: I kill you, then I take your stuff."

Kled.attackMount15.text: "You see my welcome sign back there? No? It was your friend's skull!"

Kled.attackMount16.text: "You will salute when you address me!"

Kled.attackMount18.text: "Why ain't they saluting me? They should be saluting me! Salute me now!"

Kled.attackMount19.text: "You get my invitation to visit? No? 'cause there ain't one!"

Kled.attackMount22.text: "I got your welcoming present right here!"

Kled.attackMount24.text: "Only coffin's gonna' be this lizard's belly!"

Kled.attackMount26.text: "I might have to jump off this lizard and put my boot in your watoosie!"

Kled.attackMount30.text: "My brain is on fire, my soul is strong, and my lizard is hungry!"

Kled.attackMount32.text: "He looked at me funny! Get him."

Kled.attackMount34.text: "You looking at me? 'cause I'm gonna' kill you!"

Kled.attackMount36.text: "You just justified a preemptive retaliatory strike!"

Kled.attackMount37.text: "They came looking for a fight? Let's oblige 'em."

Kled.attackMount38.text: "I am justified, and I am armed!"

Kled.attackDismount06.text: "I'll say something witty after I kill you!"

Kled.attackDismount07.text: "I'm gonna' cut you open and use your spine for a back scratcher, because it is itchy! Very itchy!"

Kled.attackDismount08.text: "I can only express myself through violence!"

Kled.attackDismount16.text: "You thought I was done? Kled ain't never done!"

Kled.attackDismount20.text: "You see, Skaarl? I'm doing it alone!"

Kled.attackDismount28.text: "You're a cockroach, and it's half-past stomping time!"

Kled.attackDismount35.text: "I'm gonna reach down your throat, and turn your lungs into mittens!"

Kled.attackDismount36.text: "I'm gonna make you wish you were a hallucination!"

Kled.attackDismount37.text: "You think I don't hear you laughing?"

Kled.attackDismount38.text: "There's fixing to be two sounds: me hitting you, and---" Kled curses.

Kled.attackDismount39.text: "Lord Colonel Major Centurion Kled don't run, no he don't!"

Kled.attackDismount40.text: "I came here to... well, I don't know what I came here for, but I'm gonna' defend it!"

Kled.moveMount01.text: "This land was made for me - and me alone."

Kled.moveMount02.text: "I hate to advocate violence and insanity, but it's worked for me."

Kled.moveMount03.text: "Were you just talking, or was it the voices again?"

Kled.moveMount04.text: "I do not want my lands tamed. I want them unruly and free."

Kled.moveMount05.text: "I'm from all over. It's next to nowhere and shut the hell up!"

Kled.moveMount06.text: "I play with guns. I work with an axe."

Kled.moveMount07.text: "Mushrooms are healthy! Once you get used to the madness and paranoia."

Kled.moveMount08.text: "A man without a weapon ain't worth listening to."

Kled.moveMount09.text: "Yeah, I like it out here. Freedom, communing with nature, killing hikers."

Kled.moveMount11.text:
"I keep hallucinating that you can talk."
 Skaarl growls
    "Nah, I'm sure it'll pass."

Kled.moveMount13.text: "Skaarl! This ain't no time for philosophying!"

Kled.moveMount14.text: "Killing a few things might loosen this up."

Kled.moveMount15.text: "No more of that! You're upsetting the invisible badgers!"

Kled.moveMount16.text: "My land begins where I walk. It ends where the sun don't shine!"

Kled.moveMount17.text: "Damn cowards, making me ride over to kill 'em."

Kled.moveMount18.text: "Well, maybe I am looking to start a fight!"

Kled.moveMount19.text: "I do prefer to ride into battle."

Kled.moveMount20.text: "Yeah, but... then how we gonna' invade both bases at once?"

Kled.moveMount21.text: "No, I'm positive, I ain't delusional!" Kled mumbles.

Kled.moveMount22.text: "Of course I'm paranoid! You tried to kill me yesterday!"

Kled.moveMount23.text: "Nah, them we kill them too! Ain't nobody on my team but you."

Kled.moveMount24.text: "I came to cut off a piece of that Noxian dream... and I ain't sharing my piece!"

Kled.moveMount25.text: "Don't try and understand 'em, just rope, throw and brand 'em."

Kled.moveMount26.text: "I grew up mean and now I'm older than murder."

Kled.moveMount27.text: "Ain't nothing more beautiful than the Noxian plains... excepting a rich corpse."

Kled.moveMount28.text: "All we need is open country, but we gonna' take everything they got!"

Kled.moveMount29.text: "I fight better when I've had my... medicine."

Kled.moveMount30.text: "No! Planning and strategy? That's city-folk stuff!"

Kled.moveMount31.text: "Don't need a plan... long as I got this axe."

Kled.moveMount32.text: "Yeah, they just confirming our suspicions, ain't they?"

Kled.moveMount33.text: "I don't have trouble communicating. Words is just treacherous bastards."

Kled.moveMount34.text: "You ready, Skaarl? This day's gonna' require some mindblowing weirdness."

Kled.moveMount35.text:
"Are you ready for anything?"
 Skaarl growls
    "Of course you are!"

Kled.moveMount37.text: "Hey, it's Forward Admiral Major Kled! I ain't been a Mister since ever!"

Kled.moveMount38.text: "Shh! Them brain weasels probably listening for us."

Kled.moveMount39.text: "Let's get to killing them interloping intruders!"

Kled.moveMount40.text: "Was the battle of Falgrim when I first took the rank of Sergeant General Colonel. Least, I think that's what rank they was. Gotta' remember to ask before killing them."

Kled.moveMount41.text: "Ain't nothing like having the wind on your back and blood on your face."

Kled.moveMount42.text: "It's your birthday, Skaarl! Let's bake a murder cake!"

Kled.moveMount43.text: "Well, my foot wanted to meet your ass, and I'm about to give them a shotgun wedding!"

Kled.moveMount44.text: "Shh! It's time to get violent... and weird."

Kled.moveMount45.text: "Oh, we find 'em, tie 'em up, then they's like a piñata full of meat."

Kled.moveMount46.text: "Damnit Skaarl, d'you hide my mushroom juice again?"

Kled.moveMount47.text: "After we finish murdering these folks, what do you think? Tacos? Yeah, tacos."

Kled.moveMount48.text: "First, we kill 'em, then we make 'em tell us where they came from."

Kled.moveMount49.text: "Remember when we sacked Trevail, and that general thought we'd be willing to share the spoils? Pheh! Officers die just as easy as anybody."

Kled.moveMount50.text: "There ain't no land that ain't mine. Just land I ain't got around to claiming."

Kled.moveMount51.text: "Just 'cause they're our team don't mean we can trust 'em."

Kled.moveMount52.text: "They're all trespassers, we're just killing them five first."

Kled.moveMount53.text:
"Yeah, yeah, invade Ionia you said, it'll be fine you said!"
 Skaarl growls
    "Fine, you said!"

Kled.moveMount55.text: "Yeah, reminds me of the siege of Rugg. Lot of men died on its high walls. It was fun."

Kled.moveMount56.text: "At the gates of Qualthala, they tried using that boiling oil on us, but you can't deep-fry courage!"

Kled.moveMount58.text: "Would you stop bitching for one minute?"

Kled.moveMount59.text: "I am deep-fried courage, and an apple pie of angry!"

Kled.moveMount60.text: "Because I know someone is trying to sneak up on us!"

Kled.moveMount61.text: "Yeah, they think they so clever! Brains don't win fights, brains is what splatter on you!"

Kled.moveMount62.text: "Well, you the only thing I trust."

Kled.moveMount65.text: "Well, just 'cause you're a hallucination and I don't speak lizard don't mean I can't understand you!"

Kled.moveMount66.text: "You do come up with the best ideas."

Kled.moveMount67.text: "No, it's when I don't drink mushroom juice that I have a problem!"

Kled.moveMount68.text: "I am Kled! High Major Commodore of the First Legion Third Multiplication Double Admiral Artillery Vanguard Company! You will respect my authority!"

Kled.moveMount69.text: "We was having a nice conversation, then they showed up... uninvited!"

Kled.moveMount70.text: "Noxus was created to train the faithful."

Kled.moveMount71.text: "What are you whining about? I already fed you half a platoon!"

Kled.moveMount73.text: "Naw, it's just like the assault on Glorft. You seen one artillery vanguard in a commando fleet action, you seen 'em all."

Kled.moveMount74.text: "Noxus ends where I say it ends."

Kled.moveMount75.text: "Ain't much I love. Only this big sky, and this dumb lizard."

Kled.moveMount77.text: "The sky is my roof, the open plains are my bed, and this lizard is the only company I need."

Kled.moveMount78.text: "This big sky, this green land. Now how could I share this with anyone?"

Kled.moveMount79.text: "Woo, it's darn pretty round here. Glad it's mine."

Kled.moveMount80.text: "You can't be lonely when the land is this beautiful."

Kled.moveDismount01.text: "This world is rough. You gotta' be tough or die."

Kled.moveDismount02.text: "Yes, a sane man would run, but I ain't the running kind!"

Kled.moveDismount05.text: "This is just a victory waiting to happen!"

Kled.moveDismount06.text: "This desert sky's gonna' open up with a rain of heavenly bloodshed and glorious violence!"

Kled.moveDismount07.text: "I am the brutal instrument of my own destiny!"

Kled.moveDismount08.text: "Ain't nobody gonna' give you nothing. Gotta' take it yourself."

Kled.moveDismount10.text: "I didn't become a Rear Forward Brigadier Admiral from running!"

Kled.moveDismount11.text: "I don't need that lizard! Kled's got his own ideas."

Kled.moveDismount12.text: "I don't need nothing but this axe... and this gun... and this hat."

Kled.moveDismount13.text: "Why's all these intruders so far away?"

Kled.moveDismount14.text: "I know that lizard ain't talking, but I still hear him. Shut up, lizard. Shut up!"

Kled.moveDismount16.text: "Hey, what was that? Of course I don't need Skaarl... but he helps."

Kled.moveDismount17.text: "What was that? Run straight into the tower?"

Kled.moveDismount18.text: "I don't need a team to start a teamfight!"

Kled.moveDismount19.text: "Sure! I'll kill all of them myself!"

Kled.moveDismount21.text: "I said I wasn't not backing off, no how!"

Kled.moveDismount22.text: "Even if I lose, I win! Just means I get to come back and kill you later!"

Kled.moveDismount23.text: "I know you're listening, brain weasels! I ain't falling for it!"

Kled.moveDismount24.text: "I am Sir Admiral Major Kled, and I smell a victory potpourri!"

Kled.moveDismount25.text: "First thing you learn as a Lieutenant Sergeant Commodore: rely only on yourself."

Kled.moveDismount28.text: "I didn't not earn the rank of Sergeant double Admiral by not running!"

Kled.moveDismount29.text: "Folks say I got violent tendencies." Kled laughs.

Kled.moveDismount30.text: "Oh, she'll see, she'll see! She'll come strolling back when I turn them interlopers into a purée."

Kled.moveDismount31.text: "Ain't nobody tough as Kled! I've got gravel in my guts and a fire in my head!"

Kled.taunt01.text: "Don't worry, them voices ain't telling me to kill you no more...! Yeah, of course we still gonna' kill 'im."

Kled.taunt02.text: "You do realise... you're on my property?"

Kled.taunt03.text: "I figure I'll help you kill 'em... before I kill you."

Kled.taunt04.text: "Usually I find conversation boring and useless. You remind me I'm right."

Kled.taunt05.text: "You feel like arguing about something? It'll make what happens later easier for you."

Kled.taunt06.text: "So... when exactly you planning on getting the hell outta' here?"

Kled.taunt07.text: "Woo, no sir, I ain't gonna' kill you and feed you to my lizard! Them's just... malicious rumours!"

Kled.taunt08.text: "Oh, before I forget, what, uh... rank are you, exactly?"

Kled.tauntNoxian01.text: "You may be from Noxus, but you ain't Noxian."

Kled.tauntNoxian03.text: "You know, I like you, brother. As much as I can like a lily-livered jungle-sniffer."

Kled.tauntNoxian04.text: "You sure you're Noxian? You look a little Ionian to me."

Kled.tauntNoxian05.text: "Watch your stepping! That's my land you're gallivanting on!"

Kled.tauntAatrox01.text: "Drinking from battle? What kind of dumb crap is that?"

Kled.tauntAatrox02.text: "Telling people you're a god? Hell, you're barely a paring knife."

Kled.tauntAatrox03.text: "Something caught in your throat? 'cause you sound desperate!"

Kled.kill01.text: "This is Noxus, son! Winner takes all!"

Kled.kill03.text: "Thought you could take my land, huh? How'd that work out for you?"

Kled.kill05.text: "Don't worry, Skaarl! We'll come back so you can eat 'em later."

Kled.kill06.text: "Whoops! Looks like I accidentally stabbed you with my long axe - until you were dead!"

Kled.kill07.text: "You were a visitor, now you're mulch!"

Kled.kill08.text: "Skaarl, that was what we call a predictable scenario."

Kled.kill09.text: "I told 'em what was gonna' happen if they came onto my land!"

Kled.kill10.text: "Next time you visit, bring more stuff I can take!"

Kled.kill11.text: "I might be a deranged lizard-riding bandito, but I whooped you real good!"

Kled.kill12.text: "Now, I might have overreacted to you unlawfully entering my property - but I don't think so!"

Kled.kill13.text: "Ahahahaha! I warned him! I did warn him!"

Kled.kill14.text: "It's funny, 'cause he died right on the border of my land, and more off my land!"

Kled.kill16.text: "Don't let the door hit you on your way to hell!"

Kled.kill20.text: "We didn't come here to teach lessons in humanity!"

Kled.kill23.text: "Nothing like a river of blood to send a message."

Kled.kill24.text: "Y'know, a long time ago, being crazy meant something."

Kled.killYordle01.text: "Just 'cause we was kin don't mean I ain't feeding you to Skaarl!"

Kled.killYordle02.text: "Hey cous', glad you came to visit!"

Kled.killYordle04.text: "Afraid I had to cut your visit short."

Kled.killYordle06.text: "Aw, you are so cute... 'fore I ripped your fuzzy head off!"

Kled.killYordle07.text: "I could feel bad about killing you, or we could stomp on your corpse!"

Kled.killAatrox01.text: "He died as dumb as he sounded."

Kled.killAatrox02.text: "And he ain't even had the indignity to call himself a demon."

Kled.killAatrox03.text: "Never had much to say, but I'm sure glad we shut him up."

Kled.killCassiopeia01.text:
"Girl was all messed up."
 Skaarl growls
    "I mean, before we killed her. Snake for legs? Crazy!"

Kled.killCassiopeia04.text: "Was that lady half-snake, or that snake half-human? She is... confusing. Dead, but confusing."

Kled.killDarius01.text: "Hey, lizard food! What exactly was you general of?"

Kled.killDarius04.text: "He wanted to unify Noxus. Guess that makes me a secessionist."

Kled.killIllaoi01.text: "Skaarl? You eatin' good tonight! That girl's got some meat on her!"

Kled.killIllaoi03.text: "I gotta' stop the mushroom juice... I swear that girl had some tentacles or something!"

Kled.killJhin02.text: "Hey, fancy pants! Got your cloak dirty!"

Kled.killJhin03.text: "I don't know what he was. I just needed him to shut up."

Kled.killJhin04.text: "I can respect crazy, but what kind of fool reloads in the middle of a fight?"

Kled.killKatarina01.text: "A sinister blade? Heck, girl, Skaarl's got farts more sinister than you was."

Kled.killKatarina02.text:
"I like a girl with moxie."
 Skaarl growls
    "No, obviously she didn't have any! That's the darn point!"

Kled.killLeBlanc01.text:
"She had one crazy getup! Them city-folk clothes is getting ridiculous."
 Skaarl growls
    "Yeah, I'll try it on later."

Kled.killLeBlanc04.text: "All your little city-girl dreams just got stomped."

Kled.killRekSai02.text: "Damn varmint left holes all over the yard."

Kled.killRekSai03.text: "Queen of what? Darn thing made Skaarl look smart!"

Kled.killRiven01.text: "Pure Noxian girl. Almost liked her. Almost."

Kled.killRiven02.text: "Seems to have lost your bounce, girl."

Kled.killRiven03.text: "All that hippy hop! Getting on my nerves!"

Kled.killSion01.text:
"How many times do I gotta' kill him?"
 Skaarl growls
    "I know!"

Kled.killSion03.text: "Too stupid to live, too dumb to die."

Kled.killSion04.text:
"I don't think you can eat that one."
 Skaarl growls
    "He looks a little overripe."

Kled.killSion06.text: "Huh. I liked him better when he was alive."

Kled.killSwain02.text: "Master Tactician? He can keep that title."

Kled.killSwain04.text:
"I figure he gonna' taste like chicken."
 Skaarl growls
    "Sure!"

Kled.killTahmKench03.text: "I knew he was a liar, 'cause he used them big words."

Kled.killTalon01.text: "I've seem some dumb outfits, Skaarl, but a cape made out of knives? Woo, ha! That took the cake!"

Kled.killTalon02.text: "Another dead city boy, thinking he could sneaky-sneak on my land."

Kled.killTalon03.text: "Let that be a lesson for all them sneaky-sneaks!"

Kled.ward01.text: "I keep my eyes open - all the time."

Kled.ward02.text: "I ain't paranoid - I'm ready. Real ready."

Kled.ward03.text: "They's always trying to sneak up on us. Trying, that is."

Kled.ward05.text: "Them sneaky-sneaks ain't gonna' sneak on us, no sir!"

Kled.ward06.text: "It's mine, and I got my eye on it!"

Kled.ward07.text: "Yeah, any of them varmints sneak up on us, we'll know."

Kled.ward08.text: "It ain't paranoia if everyone is out to get you."

Kled.ward10.text: "There's no such thing as paranoia; your worst fears can come true at any moment."

Kled.ward11.text: "Paranoia is just another word for ignorance."

Azir.unknownNasus02.text: "Let us return to our rightful place, Nasus."

Illaoi.start01.text: "It is my burden to carry an eye of god. It is my privilege to see the truth."

Illaoi.start02.text: "We cannot comprehend the design. A raindrop cannot comprehend a river valley."

Illaoi.start03.text: "To die is to drown - so I will swim well, till I can swim no more."

Illaoi.attack15.text: "Ha ha ha, you think you can beat me?"

Illaoi.attack16.text: "They need wisdom. They don't need teeth."

Illaoi.baron01.text: "I slayed greater serpents as a child."

Illaoi.baron02.text: "Here they call you a monster. In Buhru, we would call you dinner."

Illaoi.move01.text: "If I hate something, I destroy it. If I want something, I take it."

Illaoi.move02.text: "I am a teacher. Bilgewater will learn."

Illaoi.move03.text: "We are born knowing what to do. We must only act."

Illaoi.move05.text: "It is terrible to be satisfied. The world needs us to chase dreams."

Illaoi.move06.text: "This ends one of two ways - they run, or I break them."

Illaoi.move07.text: "I don't scare, I don't tire, and I don't stop."

Illaoi.move08.text: "Good? Evil? Why should we care for such things?"

Illaoi.move09.text: "Life is the sweetness of fruit, and the joy of battle!"

Illaoi.move10.text: "There is joy in food... and fighting."

Illaoi.move14.text: "Ah, everyone has a plan, until they get punched in the face."

Illaoi.move15.text: "Men live, men die. Change is good."

Illaoi.move16.text: "They will learn or they will die."

Illaoi.move17.text: "There are kind and gentle gods. Mine isn't one of those."

Illaoi.move18.text: "The ocean is calm. It is our desires that stir it."

Illaoi.move19.text: "Even if I die, I die in motion."

Illaoi.move20.text: "The waves will drag you down, unless you fight to shore."

Illaoi.move21.text: "How could I love only one man? They break too easily."

Illaoi.move23.text: "Wisdom is frequently a kick in the head."

Illaoi.move26.text: "We are not one soul. We are many."

Illaoi.move27.text: "Many gods ask for worship. They are weak gods."

Illaoi.move28.text: "My god is not love - it is a kick in the pants."

Illaoi.move29.text: "Without change, something sleeps inside us, and seldom awakens."

Illaoi.move30.text: "Many die. Worthy souls find new forms."

Illaoi.move31.text: "Bearded Lady, Nagakabouros, names don't matter! Action does."

Illaoi.move32.text: "It is the storm that is life."

Illaoi.taunt01.text: "Live your life, chase what you desire, what else matters?"

Illaoi.taunt02.text: "A fool and his spirit are easily parted."

Illaoi.taunt03.text: "Watch your mouth, or I'll slap the soul out of you."

Illaoi.taunt04.text: "Fight me, if you have the spirit."

Illaoi.taunt05.text: "I want you to hit me as hard as you can."

Illaoi.taunt06.text: "Smile, child, or I'll shove your jaw into your brain."

Illaoi.tauntAscendant01.text: "You wanted to be a god! Instead, you are a useless antique!"

Illaoi.tauntAscendant02.text: "Foul creature, you would stop time when all things must move!"

Illaoi.tauntAscendant03.text: "You soul is a fetid, stagnant pool, untouched by the tide!"

Illaoi.tauntAscendant04.text: "You are not free from death! You are dead."

Illaoi.tauntAscendant05.text: "You powers are stolen from the flow. You have damned your homeland."

Illaoi.tauntDemacia01.text: "What is truly noble and good would never ask you to serve another!"

Illaoi.tauntDemacia02.text: "Duty, honor, nations? These are stagnant falsehoods!"

Illaoi.tauntDemacia03.text: "You are slaves enchained by lies when we were born to chase our desires!"

Illaoi.tauntDemacia04.text: "Laws, rules, these are falsehoods! Truth is chaos!"

Illaoi.tauntFiora01.text: "I do not challenge you, I bring you the test!"

Illaoi.tauntGaren01.text: "Honor? Duty? Ha! What your heart demands is all that matters."

Illaoi.tauntFreljord01.text: "Your people pretend to be strong. I think they are afraid."

Illaoi.tauntFreljord02.text: "Your people seek a worthy death. Mine, a worthy life."

Illaoi.tauntBraum01.text: "Northman. There are motions I would like to show you."

Illaoi.tauntBraum02.text: "I know you are strong. I wonder if you have stamina."

Illaoi.tauntGragas02.text: "You have followed our ways as if born to them."

Illaoi.tauntShadowIsles01.text: "You are a cycle without purpose. I will end you!"
Illaoi.tauntShadowIsles01.trigger: Taunting an Enemy Shadow Isles Champion

Illaoi.tauntShadowIsles02.trigger: Taunting an Enemy Shadow Isles Champion

Illaoi.tauntShadowIsles03.text: "You are a cloud of broken souls, you are an abomination."
Illaoi.tauntShadowIsles03.trigger: Taunting an Enemy Shadow Isles Champion

Illaoi.tauntShadowIsles04.text: "You will trouble this land no more."
Illaoi.tauntShadowIsles04.trigger: Taunting an Enemy Shadow Isles Champion

Illaoi.tauntShadowIsles05.trigger: Taunting an Enemy Shadow Isles Champion

Illaoi.tauntShadowIsles06.text: "I am your enemy because you offend my god - because you cannot change."
Illaoi.tauntShadowIsles06.trigger: Taunting an Enemy Shadow Isles Champion

Illaoi.tauntShadowIsles07.text: "You will challenge me? Ha ha ha ha... even death fears my god."
Illaoi.tauntShadowIsles07.trigger: Taunting an Enemy Shadow Isles Champion

Illaoi.tauntYordle01.text: "Why would I need a spirit's help? I am guided by Nagakabouros."

Illaoi.tauntYordle02.text: "Little one, I don't need empathy. Seek those who do."

Illaoi.tauntYordle03.text: "Go back to where men are weak, and need your inspiration."

Illaoi.tauntAatrox01.text: "We know your true name. We do not fear you."

Illaoi.tauntAkali01.text: "Life is not balance. It is motion!"

Illaoi.tauntDiana01.text: "Your god was forgotten. Mine cannot be ignored."

Illaoi.tauntElise01.text: "False prophet! You don't even serve a true god!"

Illaoi.tauntDarius02.text: "You move well. Now, you must only find joy in the motion."

Illaoi.tauntGangplank01.text: "I broke men's hearts. I broke men's spines. You're the first who's going to get both."

Illaoi.tauntGangplank02.text: "You paid your tithe to the mother. Now show me what she taught you."

Illaoi.tauntGangplank03.text: "You have learned your lesson, now fight! Kill! Conquer!"

Illaoi.tauntGangplank05.text: "I do not want excuses. The failure was yours."

Illaoi.tauntGangplank06.text: "Did she not show you the way forward? Go!"

Illaoi.tauntJanna01.text: "The tempest is Nagakabouros. You serve, but are blind."

Illaoi.tauntJax01.text: "I do not challenge you, I bring you the test!"

Illaoi.tauntKarma01.text: "Trust the motion. All spirits are Nagakabouros'."

Illaoi.tauntKatarina01.text: "No love is impossible, my god demands you follow your desires."

Illaoi.tauntLeona01.text: "You worship the sun - it is my god that drives it through the sky."

Illaoi.tauntLeona02.text: "Your faith asks for obedience - it is weak."

Illaoi.tauntMissFortune02.text: "It is you who have shown Gangplank his path. For that, I thank you."

Illaoi.tauntMissFortune03.text: "Gangplank was drowning. Your actions reminded him to swim."

Illaoi.tauntRekSai01.text: "You are in motion - but only as a parasite on a host."

Illaoi.tauntRekSai02.text: "Ugly thing. You weren't designed by god, you were made by fools."

Illaoi.tauntRekSai04.text: "You are a foul creation - born from ignorance."

Illaoi.tauntRekSai05.text: "What kind of stupid god made you?"

Illaoi.tauntTahmKench01.text: "You move only from hunger that consumes itself."

Illaoi.tauntTahmKench02.text: "Creature, why would I listen to lies when I can see the truth?"

Illaoi.tauntTahmKench03.text: "Your fine words don't disguise your foul design."

Illaoi.tauntTwistedFate01.text: "Aw, child, you are cute, but I doubt you will be for long."

Illaoi.E10.text: "This is the motion. All is Nagakabouros."

Illaoi.E11.text: "I do not walk alone. I am with my god. It is here."

Illaoi.E12.text: "You cannot hide from god. You cannot hide from the test."

Illaoi.vessel01.text: "Live your journey - or die in mine."
Illaoi.vessel01.trigger: When a Champion Becomes a Vessel

Illaoi.vessel02.text: "Your spirit is held - take it if you can."
Illaoi.vessel02.trigger: When a Champion Becomes a Vessel

Illaoi.vessel03.trigger: When a Champion Becomes a Vessel

Illaoi.vessel04.text: "You speak of having a soul. It was never yours. None of them were."
Illaoi.vessel04.trigger: When a Champion Becomes a Vessel

Illaoi.vessel05.trigger: When a Champion Becomes a Vessel

Illaoi.vessel06.text: "Change, or you will be pulled down."
Illaoi.vessel06.trigger: When a Champion Becomes a Vessel

Illaoi.vessel07.trigger: When a Champion Becomes a Vessel

Illaoi.vessel08.text: "You are drowning - I want you to swim."
Illaoi.vessel08.trigger: When a Champion Becomes a Vessel

Illaoi.vessel09.trigger: When a Champion Becomes a Vessel

Illaoi.vessel10.trigger: When a Champion Becomes a Vessel

Illaoi.vessel11.text: "Each of your lives has served the vortex."
Illaoi.vessel11.trigger: When a Champion Becomes a Vessel

Illaoi.vessel12.trigger: When a Champion Becomes a Vessel

Illaoi.vessel13.text: "We learn from action. Move, or die."
Illaoi.vessel13.trigger: When a Champion Becomes a Vessel

Illaoi.vessel14.trigger: When a Champion Becomes a Vessel

Illaoi.vessel15.text: "This will be a good day - if you live."
Illaoi.vessel15.trigger: When a Champion Becomes a Vessel

Illaoi.vessel16.text: "Drive forward - it is destiny that calls you."
Illaoi.vessel16.trigger: When a Champion Becomes a Vessel

Illaoi.vessel17.trigger: When a Champion Becomes a Vessel

Illaoi.vessel18.trigger: When a Champion Becomes a Vessel

Illaoi.vessel19.trigger: When a Champion Becomes a Vessel

Illaoi.vessel20.text: "My god doesn't want you to kneel. It wants you to fight."
Illaoi.vessel20.trigger: When a Champion Becomes a Vessel

Illaoi.vessel21.text: "You have been given the tools to know your destiny."
Illaoi.vessel21.trigger: When a Champion Becomes a Vessel

Illaoi.vessel22.text: "The failure of your lives is written on your soul."
Illaoi.vessel22.trigger: When a Champion Becomes a Vessel

Illaoi.vessel23.trigger: When a Champion Becomes a Vessel

Illaoi.vessel24.text: "We are all free. Seeing the truth only reminds us."
Illaoi.vessel24.trigger: When a Champion Becomes a Vessel

Illaoi.vessel25.trigger: When a Champion Becomes a Vessel

Illaoi.vessel26.text: "All of us are lost, all of us are blind. You must swim towards your destiny."
Illaoi.vessel26.trigger: When a Champion Becomes a Vessel

Illaoi.vessel27.text: "Countless lifetimes lead our bodies foward, and drive our spirits towards their true destiny."
Illaoi.vessel27.trigger: When a Champion Becomes a Vessel

Illaoi.vessel28.text: "I don't want you to fail, I want you to learn."
Illaoi.vessel28.trigger: When a Champion Becomes a Vessel

Illaoi.vessel29.text: "Child, you must earn your soul. Prove yourself."
Illaoi.vessel29.trigger: When a Champion Becomes a Vessel

Illaoi.vessel30.text: "The battle is lost only when you surrender. Fight for your soul."
Illaoi.vessel30.trigger: When a Champion Becomes a Vessel

Illaoi.vessel31.text: "You are the tinest sliver of energy held briefly in shape. Where this energy flows is your destiny."
Illaoi.vessel31.trigger: When a Champion Becomes a Vessel

Illaoi.vessel32.text: "This moment is waiting to be seized."
Illaoi.vessel32.trigger: When a Champion Becomes a Vessel

Illaoi.vessel33.text: "Every day is waiting to be taken."
Illaoi.vessel33.trigger: When a Champion Becomes a Vessel

Illaoi.vessel34.text: "I don't want you to worship. I want you to learn."
Illaoi.vessel34.trigger: When a Champion Becomes a Vessel

Illaoi.vessel35.text: "I will break you if that's what it takes."
Illaoi.vessel35.trigger: When a Champion Becomes a Vessel

Illaoi.vessel36.text: "Give up, and your life is nothing."
Illaoi.vessel36.trigger: When a Champion Becomes a Vessel

Illaoi.vessel37.text: "Each lifetime is a spirit. Each lifetime is a chance. Take it."
Illaoi.vessel37.trigger: When a Champion Becomes a Vessel

Illaoi.vesselTentacle01.trigger: While a Champion is a Vessel

Illaoi.vesselTentacle02.trigger: While a Champion is a Vessel

Illaoi.vesselTentacle03.trigger: While a Champion is a Vessel

Illaoi.vesselTentacle04.trigger: While a Champion is a Vessel

Illaoi.vesselTentacle05.trigger: While a Champion is a Vessel

Illaoi.vesselTentacle06.trigger: While a Champion is a Vessel

Illaoi.vesselTentacle07.text: "Do not tire, do not slow, push onward."
Illaoi.vesselTentacle07.trigger: While a Champion is a Vessel

Illaoi.vesselTentacle08.text: "Exactly. If you want your soul, take it."
Illaoi.vesselTentacle08.trigger: While a Champion is a Vessel

Illaoi.vesselTentacle09.text: "Keep going, keep striving. This is our way."
Illaoi.vesselTentacle09.trigger: While a Champion is a Vessel

Illaoi.vesselTentacle10.trigger: While a Champion is a Vessel

Illaoi.vesselTentacle11.trigger: While a Champion is a Vessel

Illaoi.vesselTentacle12.trigger: While a Champion is a Vessel

Illaoi.vesselTentacle13.text: "Your souls wait for you. Take them back if you can."
Illaoi.vesselTentacle13.trigger: While a Champion is a Vessel

Illaoi.vesselTentacle14.text: "This is the way of Nagakabouros - motion!"
Illaoi.vesselTentacle14.trigger: While a Champion is a Vessel

Illaoi.vesselTentacle15.trigger: While a Champion is a Vessel

Illaoi.vesselTentacle16.text: "To challenge, to fight... this pleases Nagakabouros."
Illaoi.vesselTentacle16.trigger: While a Champion is a Vessel

Illaoi.vesselFreedom01.trigger: When a Champion Stops Being a Vessel

Illaoi.vesselFreedom02.text: "Pray I don't have to teach you again."
Illaoi.vesselFreedom02.trigger: When a Champion Stops Being a Vessel

Illaoi.vesselFreedom03.trigger: When a Champion Stops Being a Vessel

Illaoi.vesselFreedom04.trigger: When a Champion Stops Being a Vessel

Illaoi.vesselFreedom05.text: "Learn well, or you will be tested again."
Illaoi.vesselFreedom05.trigger: When a Champion Stops Being a Vessel

Illaoi.vesselFreedom06.trigger: When a Champion Stops Being a Vessel

Illaoi.vesselFreedom07.text: "You have been tested. You have done well."
Illaoi.vesselFreedom07.trigger: When a Champion Stops Being a Vessel

Illaoi.vesselFreedom08.trigger: When a Champion Stops Being a Vessel

Illaoi.vesselFreedom09.text: "Did you blunder into victory, or did you learn?"
Illaoi.vesselFreedom09.trigger: When a Champion Stops Being a Vessel

Illaoi.item01.text: "It is not what we have, it is what we can throw away."

Illaoi.item02.text: "Things should be held only when we need them."

Illaoi.item03.text: "Only what moves, only what lives... has value."

Illaoi.item04.text: "When I am done with this... it will make a fine offering."

Illaoi.item05.text: "I like this. I should buy everyone one of these."

Illaoi.itemBootsBasic01.text: "I am going to walk all over them."

Illaoi.itemBootsAdvanced01.text: "My god is motion, but speed is useful."

Illaoi.itemRanduinsOmen01.text: "Who is Randuin? Was she a priestess?"

Illaoi.itemSteraksGage01.text: "Sterak? It is the fury of the mother I will bring."

Illaoi.itemTitanicHydra01.text: "The Kraken. The Serpent. The Hydra. A god's appearance is limited only by those observing it."

Illaoi.itemWarmogs01.text: "It is my god that protects me - but these metal clothes are nice."

Rakan.start01.text: "My fellow travelers, you are all about to witness my majestic epicness! ... unless I get killed, but... probably not!"

Rakan.start02.text: "Okay, everybody, I'm here, I'm here... the party starts now!"

Rakan.start03.text: "Magic is in the heart. Magic is in the rhythm."

Rakan.start04.text: "You see this cape? Ha! I say goddamn I'm sexy!"

Rakan.start05.text: "I can't wait to get in there. I don't know what I'm going to do, but I am going to get in there!"

Rakan.start06.text: "Xayah? Xayah? Crap. What was I supposed to do?"

Rakan.start09.text: "Consequences only matter if I don't get away."

Rakan.start10.text: "We are seen dancing and thought insane - by those who can't hear the music."

Rakan.startXayah01.text:
Rakan: "Alright, let's go! This way or that way?"
 Xayah: "Stick to the plan."
 Rakan: "We have a plan?"
 Xayah: "We always have a plan."
 Rakan: "Huh. Really?"
Rakan.startXayah01.trigger: Upon Starting a Game with Xayah

Rakan.startXayah02.text:
Xayah: "Ugh, I hate everyone today."
 Rakan: "I know what'll make you feel better... "
 Xayah and Rakan: "Murdering everyone!"
Rakan.startXayah02.trigger: Upon Starting a Game with Xayah

Rakan.startXayah03.text:
Rakan: "Hey, I have a plan."
 Xayah: "You... have a plan?"
 Rakan: "Yeah! I'll go on instinct!"
 Xayah: "That's the opposite of a plan."
Rakan.startXayah03.trigger: Upon Starting a Game with Xayah

Rakan.startXayah04.text:
Rakan: "You sure about this?"
 Xayah: "It has to be done."
 Rakan: "Be safe."
 Xayah: "Like you can talk."
Rakan.startXayah04.trigger: Upon Starting a Game with Xayah

Rakan.startXayah05.text:
Xayah: "If things go wrong---"
 Rakan: "They always go wrong."
 Xayah: "They don't always go wrong."
 Rakan: "Mostly?"
 Xayah: "They mostly go wrong."
 Rakan: "That's why I'm here."
Rakan.startXayah05.trigger: Upon Starting a Game with Xayah

Rakan.startXayah06.text:
Rakan: "So, this mission... are we, uh...?"
 Xayah: "Are you pretending to be dumb?"
 Rakan: "Well, I mean... I don't have to remember the plan if you do."
Rakan.startXayah06.trigger: Upon Starting a Game with Xayah

Rakan.startXayah07.text:
Rakan: "When are we going to do this?"
 Xayah: "Soon, baby. Slow down."
Rakan.startXayah07.trigger: Upon Starting a Game with Xayah

Rakan.attack08.text: "It ain't a party without a fight!"

Rakan.attack13.text: "I got one more thing for you!"

Rakan.attack23.text: "You will see the dance of death."

Rakan.attack32.text: "Hey! I got a joke for you!"

Rakan.attack36.text: "Oh! I need to get in there!"

Rakan.attack37.text: "Hey, what did the five fingers say to the face?"

Rakan.attack53.text: "I like parties with a little violence!"

Rakan.attack56.text: "I have killed for her! I will kill for her again."

Rakan.attack62.text: "Count it down! One, two, they dead!"

Rakan.attack63.text: "I'm here! We can get it started!"

 Rakan: "I can't hear you over all the fun I'm having!"
Rakan.attackXayah01.trigger: While an Allied Xayah is Nearby

Rakan.attackXayah02.text:
Rakan: "The fight's here!, by me!"
 Xayah: "It's the same fight!"
Rakan.attackXayah02.trigger: While an Allied Xayah is Nearby

Rakan.attackXayah03.trigger: While an Allied Xayah is Nearby

Rakan.attackXayah04.text:
Xayah: "I hate everyone today!"
 Rakan: "Even me?"
 Xayah: "Not you, baby."
Rakan.attackXayah04.trigger: While an Allied Xayah is Nearby

Rakan.attackXayah05.text:
Rakan: "Should we give them a fighting chance?"
 Xayah: "Only if we want to have fun."
Rakan.attackXayah05.trigger: While an Allied Xayah is Nearby

Rakan.attackXayah06.text:
Rakan: "Who do I hit?"
 Xayah: "One of them!"
 Rakan: "Ah."
Rakan.attackXayah06.trigger: While an Allied Xayah is Nearby

Rakan.attackXayah07.text:
Xayah: "This reminds me of our first dates!"
 Rakan: "Good times!"
Rakan.attackXayah07.trigger: While an Allied Xayah is Nearby

Rakan.attackXayah08.text:
Xayah: "Mind if I cut in, Rakan?"
 Rakan: " Be my guest, miella!"
Rakan.attackXayah08.trigger: While an Allied Xayah is Nearby

Rakan.attackXayah09.trigger: While an Allied Xayah is Nearby

Rakan.attackXayah10.text:
Rakan: "You see that?"
 Xayah: "I couldn't miss it!"
Rakan.attackXayah10.trigger: While an Allied Xayah is Nearby

Rakan.attackXayah11.text:
Xayah: "Make them remember!"
 Rakan: "They'll never forget."
Rakan.attackXayah11.trigger: While an Allied Xayah is Nearby

Rakan.attackXayah12.text:
Xayah: "Let's show 'em what we got."
 Rakan: "Happily."
Rakan.attackXayah12.trigger: While an Allied Xayah is Nearby

Rakan.attackXayah13.text:
Rakan: "You love it when I slap fools?"
 Xayah: "You know I do!"
Rakan.attackXayah13.trigger: While an Allied Xayah is Nearby

Rakan.attackXayah14.text:
Rakan: "This is the plan, right?"
 Xayah: "It is now!"
Rakan.attackXayah14.trigger: While an Allied Xayah is Nearby

Rakan.attackXayah15.text:
Rakan: "What do you want to do later?"
 Xayah: "I can think of something."
Rakan.attackXayah15.trigger: While an Allied Xayah is Nearby

Rakan.attackXayah16.text:
Rakan: "You hungry?"
 Xayah: "Can we talk about this later?"
 Rakan: "But... but... food!"
Rakan.attackXayah16.trigger: While an Allied Xayah is Nearby

Rakan.attackXayah17.text:
Xayah: "You're cute today!"
 Rakan: "Eyes on the prize, baby."
Rakan.attackXayah17.trigger: While an Allied Xayah is Nearby

Rakan.attackXayah18.text:
Rakan: "Let me at 'em!"
 Xayah: "Rakan is very enthusiastic."
Rakan.attackXayah18.trigger: While an Allied Xayah is Nearby

Rakan.attackXayah19.text:

Rakan.move01.text: "Our magic is a fury. It is a song you cannot resist."

Rakan.move02.text: "Should I be... running? Yeah, I should... probably be running."

Rakan.move03.text: "I look around these forests and I see freedom. I hear the music."

Rakan.move04.text: "Crap. I totally forgot why I'm here."

Rakan.move05.text: "I am only as wild as magic."

Rakan.move06.text: "Magic is supposed to be scary. Love is supposed to hurt. Ecstasy needs a little fear."

Rakan.move07.text: "If you aren't a little frightened, you ain't alive."

Rakan.move10.text: "Humans made promises. More than I can remember. They kept none."

Rakan.move11.text: "Humans talk about their treaties. We talk about their lies."

Rakan.move12.text: "Long ago, our kind danced upon the mountains like flames. Now only the embers remain."

Rakan.move14.text: "The only way to understand magic is to plunge into it, move with it, dance and dance!"

Rakan.move16.text: "Gotta get myself hyped, okay... one, two... one, two... woo! Alright!"

Rakan.move17.text: "The humans call it battle. It's just a dance."

Rakan.move18.text: "I feel like my allies aren't recognising how amazing my cloak is! I mean, seriously! Rude!"

Rakan.move19.text: "They will see my dance, then they will know magic's joy... and its fury."

Rakan.move20.text: "Okay, Rakan, get 'em watching you, then you burn 'em up."

Rakan.move21.text: "I look good, I feel good, let's kick some ass!"

Rakan.move22.text: "I got my look right, I got my moves right... time to show it!"

Rakan.move25.text: "I'm going to take all they got, then laugh as I throw it away."

Rakan.move26.text: "I've been kicked around since I was born. It's alright! It's okay! I'm staying alive!"

Rakan.move27.text: "They will see me. They will see my dance!"

Rakan.move28.text: "I will walk in. I will dance. They will party."

Rakan.move30.text: "Ha! I'm G to the D! Golden diamonds, boy! Woo!"

Rakan.move31.text: "I'm just trying to live the moment."

Rakan.move32.text: "I don't need anything - but the right now."

Rakan.move34.text: "Man, have you seen that forest over there?"

Rakan.move35.text: "I got freedom, I got a lady, I got a cause I'd die for. That's who I am."

Rakan.move38.text: "I don't need to understand the plan! I trust my love."

Rakan.move39.text: "It's all filthy and dangerous - and that's why I love it!"

Rakan.move42.text: "Why is it taking so long to get back to the action?"

Rakan.move43.text: "It's a revolution. And it's good times."

Rakan.move44.text: "I'm offended by how little attention I was given."

Rakan.move45.text: "Humans think that to believe in something, you have to be serious about it. That's their problem."

Rakan.move46.text: "They ain't ready for what I'm bringing!"

Rakan.move47.text: "Ain't nothing I say should be taken seriously! That's why it's the truth!"

Rakan.move49.text: "This looks like another dangerous situation. Thankfully, I can improvise."

Rakan.move50.text: "They're gonna' try and test me? Haha!"

Rakan.move51.text: "Danger is as fun as you let it be."

Rakan.move52.text: "I am definitely more confident in dangerous situations."

Rakan.move53.text: "I have got to stop talking to myself. Damnit, Xayah, where are you?"

Rakan.move54.text: "You're only given a little spark of madness. You mustn't lose it."

Rakan.move55.text: "I can't wait to see what I'm going to do."

Rakan.move56.text: "There's wildness in the bees and the flowers. It's just a fury humans don't see."

Rakan.move57.text: "I am Vastaya. I am born of magic. This is my destiny."

Rakan.move58.text: "Is my cloak right? Yes it is! I was worried there for a second."

Rakan.move60.text: "They're scared of darkness, they're scared of magic. They are scared of where I'm from."

Rakan.move62.text: "It's magic that's wild. I'm just here for the party."

Rakan.move63.text: "For humans, magic is like fire. For us, it is water and air."

Rakan.move64.text: "Ladies and gentleman, I am here to entertain! Myself, mostly - but you too!"

Rakan.move65.text: "Humans claim it is theirs. They fence us away and cover it in refuse."

Rakan.move66.text: "It don't take a lot of words to tell the truth."

Rakan.move67.text: "Our people are bleeding. My lady's gonna' heal them."

Rakan.move68.text: "I don't want a world that's safe."

Rakan.move69.text: "I don't want a war - but I want to be free."

Rakan.move70.text: "What human's call magic, we call life."

Rakan.move71.text: "I'm here! I'm gone, I am so gone."

Rakan.move75.text: "If Xayah says someone has to die, they die - and they deserved it."

Rakan.move76.text: "Woo! I am so into this! What is this?"

Rakan.move77.text: "If it don't get out of control, it ain't a party."

Rakan.move78.text: "I think they underestimate my charm. How is that even possible?"

Rakan.move79.text: "I'm so fine, I gotta kiss myself!"

Rakan.move83.text: "They want us in cages. We refuse."

Rakan.move84.text: "I need my love to hurt. I need the world to be scary. I don't apologise for it! I feel good!"

Rakan.move85.text: "I'm gonna' burn this place down, then help them build it back up - so I can burn it again!"

Rakan.move87.text: "Xayah? Hey! Damn, where is she? I hate it when she leaves."

Rakan.move88.text: "Without wild magic, we have no children, we have no future."

Rakan.move89.text: "When I get sad, I stop being sad and be awesome instead. True story."

Rakan.move90.text: "I do not wish to kill the mortals. I want them to hear the music."

Rakan.move91.text: "The humans will never understand our kind until they hear the song."

Rakan.move92.text: "I will make them dance. I will make them hear."

Rakan.killSwain04.text: "Power was not meant to be contained. Now, it is free."

Rakan.killSwain05.text: "You were given Vastayan blood, yet chose to be blind."

Rakan.killUdyr01.text: "It is from our blood your gifts came, and my hand that took it back."

Rakan.killIllaoi01.text: "What was with that girl's dumb purse?"

Rakan.killIllaoi02.text: "Girl thought she could pull out my soul - but I got too much soul!"

Rakan.killIllaoi03.text: "Big girl had too much going on."

Rakan.killRekSai02.text: "Was that a land shark? I mean, why? Why is that a thing?"

Rakan.killRekSai03.text: "Perfect predator? I got an instinct about how stupid that thing was."

Rakan.ward01.text: "I need to see if people can see how awesome I am!"

Rakan.ward02.text: "When you open your eyes, you see everything is limitless."

Rakan.ward03.text: "I need to know when the action's coming."

Rakan.ward04.text: "Well I don't want to miss the start of the party."

Rakan.ward06.text: "The world's a big place. Don't want to miss any of it."

Rakan.ward07.text: "I'm pretty sure I'm supposed to scout around. Pretty, pretty sure."

Rakan.ward08.text: "I'll just put that there. That's a good place. I hope. Yeah... "

Rakan.ward10.text: "Yep, if I'm going to see the human world I need to start."

Rakan.ward11.text: "I'm going to show people some of the strange."

Rakan.ward13.text: "I am not blind to any possibility."

Rakan.ward14.text: "I know people are watching. How could they not be?"

Rakan.ward15.text: "If you look at things the right way, it's awesome."

Rakan.ward16.text: "The world isn't about collecting stuff, it's about seeing stuff."

Rakan.ward19.text: "Mankind is blind. I want them to see."

Rakan.ward20.text: "Vision is the first step towards understanding."

Rakan.ward21.text: "Aw, crap, I hate having to have a plan."

Rakan.ward23.text: "I think Xayah told me to improvise. At least, that's the only part of the plan I remember."

Rakan.ward24.text: "Let's see what these animals can do."

Rakan.ward26.text: "Our kind will see the truth soon enough."

Rakan.ward27.text: "I want to feel everything. That's the only way to live."

Rakan.ward31.text: "I should totally get paid for this."

Xayah.start01.text: "If love is feeling so deeply for another that you want to chew your way under their skin, then I love Rakan... "

Xayah.start02.text: "The Vastayan named the world. We named the trees, the wind, the mountains. We know their power."

Xayah.start03.text: "The world owes the Vastaya a great debt. I'm here to collect."

Xayah.start04.text: "I'm just an ordinary girl. An ordinary girl with an infinite supply of death quills."

Xayah.start05.text: "They'll probably label me a war criminal one day, but not today."

Xayah.start06.text: "We pledged ourselves to each other in the middle of a tavern brawl. The whole place reeked of vomit, sweat and blood. It was so romantic!"

Xayah.start07.text: "Ah, silence, so golden. Like Rakan. Kind of miss him. Even if he is... noisy."

Xayah.move01.text: "Sabotage takes patience and time - and lots of feather daggers."

Xayah.move02.text: "I'll do whatever needs to be done - twice, just to be sure."

Xayah.move04.text: "Oh, I was born to ruffle feathers."

Xayah.move05.text: "Our Vastayan essence fades with each passing day."

Xayah.move06.text: "I will rest when our homelands are restored."

Xayah.move07.text: "All women desire Rakan. Like they'd know what to do with him."

Xayah.move08.text: "They say I don't know when to quit. Like that's a weakness."

Xayah.move09.text: "We Vastaya are only half of our full glory."

Xayah.move10.text: "Rebellion puts the fire in my blood."

Xayah.move12.text: "Talking to anybody about anything is never on my to-do list."

Xayah.move13.text: "If our existence is everyone else's chaos, so be it."

Xayah.move14.text: "Talking to people makes me want to stab them... so I do."

Xayah.move15.text: "Victors are the sole authors of history. Time to write our chapter."

Xayah.move16.text: "Tavern brawls just seem to find me."

Xayah.move17.text: "Chaos is the preferred state of nature."

Xayah.move19.text: "Nature bends towards chaos. Give in, or break."

Xayah.move20.text: "I really hate anyone who's not me - or Rakan."

Xayah.move21.text: "Nature is wild and untamed, not balanced."

Xayah.move24.text: "If Rakan were here, I'd make out with him until his ears bled. He loves it when I do that."

Xayah.move26.text: "Magic is not some river that can be easily channeled. It is a churning sea that goes where it pleases."

Xayah.move27.text: "I hate flowers. Tiny skulls stuffed with twigs, on the other hand... "

Xayah.move28.text: "Sometimes people die for a good cause - namely, mine. That's why I'm an optimist."

Xayah.move30.text: "I prefer to work at night, because, y'know, the sun? Bright? Yuck!"

Xayah.move31.text: "Pandemonium follows me everywhere I go. It's like a puppy I once fed... "

Xayah.move32.text: "Ionia used to be so nice - before humans tamed all that wild cataclysmic magic."

Xayah.move33.text: "Once, magic was everywhere, or as the Vastaya say: (chants)"
